Traditional Artistry and Craftsmanship</h2>\\nOne of the most striking features of the Multipurpose Ayurveda Table is its traditional design, which is a nod to the rich heritage of Ayurveda. Skilled Indian craftsmen have poured their expertise into every detail of this table, ensuring that it not only serves its functional purpose but also exudes an air of timeless elegance.\\n<h2>Exquisite Hand Carvings: A Testament to Skilled Artisans</h2>\\nThe side frames and legs of the table are adorned with exquisite hand carvings, showcasing the craftsmanship of skilled artisans. These intricate designs not only add to the visual appeal of the table but also serve as a reminder of the centuries-old tradition of craftsmanship that is synonymous with Ayurveda.\\n<h2>Elevating Aesthetics with Rustic Brass Ornamentation</h2>\\nTo further enhance its aesthetic appeal, the Multipurpose Ayurveda Table features rustic brass ornamentation on the handle and Shirodhara Oil Stand. These subtle yet elegant touches elevate the overall aesthetics of the table, making it a focal point of any Ayurvedic set-up.\\n<h2>The Versatility of the Multipurpose Ayurveda Table</h2>\\nWhile its primary purpose may be for performing Ayurvedic massages and treatments, the Multipurpose Ayurveda Bed offers much more versatility than meets the eye. You can use it as <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/shirodhara-bed/\\">Shirodhara Table</a> and its features and curated collection of accessories make it suitable for a variety of therapeutic practices, ensuring that it remains a valuable asset in any wellness center or spa.\\n<h2>Enhancing Ayurvedic Set-Ups with Traditional Design</h2>\\nIn addition to its functional benefits, the Multipurpose Ayurveda Table also serves to enhance the ambience of any Ayurvedic set-up. Its traditional design and exquisite craftsmanship create an atmosphere of authenticity and reverence for the ancient tradition of Ayurveda, making it the perfect centerpiece for any wellness space.\\n<h2>Benefits of Using a Purpose-Designed Ayurveda Massage Table</h2>\\nFacilitates proper body alignment during massages, ensuring maximum therapeutic benefit:\\n\\n• The design of the Ayurveda Massage Table prioritizes proper body alignment, allowing both the practitioner and the client to benefit fully from the massage.\\n• With its ergonomic features and thoughtful design, the table supports the body in a way that promotes relaxation and enhances the effectiveness of massage techniques.\\n• Proper alignment ensures that pressure is distributed evenly across the body, minimizing strain on specific areas and facilitating a deeper sense of relaxation and rejuvenation.\\n<h2>Adjustable settings accommodate practitioners of varying heights and clients with different needs:</h2>\\n• The versatility of the purpose-designed Ayurveda Massage Table lies in its design, which caters to the diverse needs of both practitioners and clients.\\n\\n• Practitioners can utilize the mattress for floor massages or normal dry massages\\n• Clients with specific requirements, such as those with mobility issues or physical limitations, can also benefit from the WOODEN STEP to get on and off the table\\n<h3>Durable construction ensures longevity, making it a worthwhile investment for any wellness center or spa:</h3>\\n• Crafted with high-quality materials and expert craftsmanship, the Ayurveda Massage Table is built to withstand the rigors of daily use in a professional spa or wellness center.\\n• The durability of the table ensures that it remains in optimal condition over time, reducing the need for frequent repairs or replacements.\\n• Investing in a purpose-designed Massage Table with <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/shirodhara-stand/\\">Shirodhara Stand</a> is a wise decision for any business owner looking to create a lasting and reliable foundation for their practice.\\n<h3>Enhances the overall client experience, leading to greater satisfaction and repeat business:</h3>\\n• The comfort and functionality of the Ayurveda Massage Table contribute significantly to the overall client experience, fostering a sense of relaxation and well-being from the moment they step into the treatment room.\\n• Clients appreciate the attention to detail and thoughtful design elements that enhance their comfort and allow them to fully immerse themselves in the healing benefits of the massage.\\n• A positive experience on the massage table increases client satisfaction and loyalty, leading to repeat business and positive word-of-mouth referrals.\\n<h3>Contributes to the authenticity and professionalism of your Ayurvedic practice, helping you stand out in a competitive market:</h3>\\n• As an essential tool in Ayurvedic therapy, the purpose-designed <a href=\\"https://www.wikipedia.org/\\">Ayurveda</a> Massage Table communicates a commitment to authenticity and professionalism in your practice.\\n• Its traditional design elements and functionality align with the principles of Ayurveda, resonating with clients seeking an authentic and holistic approach to wellness.\\n• By investing in a high-quality Ayurveda Massage Table, you demonstrate your dedication to providing an exceptional standard of care, setting your practice apart in a competitive market and attracting discerning clients who value quality and authenticity.\\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\\nThe Multipurpose <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/multipurpose-ayurveda-table/\\">Ayurveda Massage Table</a> is more than just a piece of furniture – it is a symbol of authenticity, tradition, and craftsmanship. By investing in this purpose-designed table, you can elevate the quality of your Ayurvedic practice and create an experience that is truly unforgettable for your clients. So why settle for anything less when you can have the best? Choose the Multipurpose Ayurveda Table and embark on a journey of holistic healing like never before.\\n\\n&nbsp;\\n\\n&nbsp;\\n\\n&nbsp;"	cmqagwwrv01ascgtnsfq22szf	cmq0jhmi20000cgcbtc248zz0	estheticaspafurniture	PUBLISHED	2024-04-18 15:28:34	\N	Ayurveda Massage Table: Elevate Your Ayurvedic Practice	Elevate your Ayurvedic practice with the Multipurpose Ayurveda Massage Table. Tailor-made for oil massages and Shirodhara treatments.	{"Ayurveda Massage Table","Ayurvedic Massage Table"}	\N	Ayurveda Massage Table: Elevate Your Ayurvedic Practice	Elevate your Ayurvedic practice with the Multipurpose Ayurveda Massage Table. Tailor-made for oil massages and Shirodhara treatments.	\N	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 07:15:58.379	2026-06-12 05:19:31.558
cmq0lbhag04ftcgcbmlf6fjk3	A comprehensive guide to the art and science of massage tables.	comprehensive-guide-art-science-massage-tables	Massage therapy has evolved as an essential component of holistic wellness practices globally, providing both physical and emotional health advantages. The massage table is an essential component of any effective massage session. The massage table , sometimes underestimated but essential, plays an e…	"<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Massage therapy has evolved as an essential component of holistic wellness practices globally, providing both physical and emotional health advantages. The massage table is an essential component of any effective massage session. The <strong><a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/massage-tables/\\">massage table</a>, </strong>sometimes underestimated but essential, plays an essential role in guaranteeing both the client's comfort and the effectiveness of the massage technique.</p>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">This detailed guide goes into the fine elements of massage tables from your very own <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/\\"><em><strong>Esthetica Spa and Salon Resources Pvt. Ltd</strong>,</em></a> including their design, functionality, materials, and major features.</p>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><img class=\\"aligncenter\\" src=\\"/uploads/wp-legacy/2016/07/MANAK-1-1-1024x738.jpg\\" alt=\\"Manak Electric Spa Massage Table\\" width=\\"526\\" height=\\"379\\" /></p>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Understanding the Anatomy of a Massage Table</h2>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Understanding massage table anatomy is vital for appreciating its intricacies. A standard massage table is made up of various parts and components, including a frame structure, padding, upholstery, electric motors, and other electrical components OR it can be a simple wooden massage bed without electric motors and electronic components. The frame acts as a foundation, giving stability and support during massage treatments. High-quality frames for wooden massage tables are made using tenon &amp; mortise joinery which is one of the strongest jointing techniques and subsequently has been used by cabinetmakers and joiners for generations. The <strong><a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/manak-electric-spa-massage-table/\\">electric spa treatment table </a></strong>frames are a combination wooden frame structure reinforced with a tubular metal frame inside for motorized height, backrest, leg rest and Trendelenburg functions.</p>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Exploring Materials and Construction</h2>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">The materials used for massage tables have a considerable impact on their longevity, comfort, and portability. Wood, known for its inherent warmth and beauty, is still a popular choice for massage table frames. Furthermore, padding and upholstery materials play an important role in maintaining client comfort. Clients benefit from a sturdy and inviting surface made of high-density foam cushioning and durable yet soft upholstery. A fire retardant and disinfectant-resistant upholstery are the new requirements of premium spa setups.</p>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Understanding Table Features and Adjustments</h2>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Massage tables include a variety of features meant to improve functionality and versatility. Adjustable height settings enable practitioners to tailor the table to their chosen working height, supporting clients of varied sizes and interests. Furthermore, distinctive features like adjustable backrests, adjustable leg &amp; knee positions, face cradles, armrests, and side arm extensions provide extra comfort and support during massage sessions. By understanding and utilizing these aspects, practitioners can optimize their workplace and improve the client experience.</p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>Adjustable Height</strong></h3>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Most tables and <strong><a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/massage-beds/\\">massage Beds</a> </strong>feature adjustable height settings, allowing practitioners to customize the table to their preferred working height. This feature is essential for accommodating practitioners of different heights and ensuring ergonomic body mechanics during massage sessions. Adjustable height settings also allow practitioners to raise or lower the table to accommodate clients of varying sizes and mobility levels.</p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>Face Cradle</strong></h3>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">A face cradle is a removable attachment that attaches to the end of the massage table and supports the client's head and neck in a face-down position. Face cradles typically feature adjustable angles and cushioning to provide optimal comfort and support for clients during massage sessions. Face cradles are essential for allowing clients to relax fully during face-down massage techniques such as prone massage and craniosacral therapy.</p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>Armrests</strong></h3>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Armrests provide support for the client's arms during massage sessions, reducing tension in the shoulders and wrists. Adjustable armrests allow clients to customize their arm support for maximum comfort and relaxation. Some <a href=\\"https://www.portablemassagebed.in/\\">massage tables</a> feature detachable or adjustable armrests to accommodate clients of different sizes and preferences.</p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>Side Arm Extensions</strong></h3>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Side arm extensions provide additional width to the massage table, allowing clients with broader shoulders or those who prefer to lie with their arms by their sides to relax comfortably. Side arm extensions are particularly beneficial for clients receiving modalities such as sports massage or deep tissue massage, where the arms may be positioned close to the body.</p>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Ensuring Durability and Longevity</h2>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Investing in a <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/\\">high-quality massage table</a> is essential to ensure durability and longevity, minimizing the need for frequent replacements and repairs. Factors such as frame construction, material quality, and craftsmanship all contribute to the overall durability of the table. Regular maintenance, including cleaning and inspection of components, further extends the lifespan of the table, preserving its functionality and appearance for years to come.</p>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Considering Client Comfort and Safety</h2>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Client comfort and safety should always remain paramount considerations when selecting and using a massage table. The table's design should promote proper body alignment and support, reducing the risk of discomfort or injury during massage sessions. Additionally, attention to detail, such as rounded corners and warning labels on the pinch points, proper earthing, and electrical safety devices enhance safety and minimize the risk of accidents or mishaps. By prioritizing client well-being, practitioners can foster trust and satisfaction, ensuring a positive and rewarding experience for all involved.</p>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Conclusion</h2>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">The massage table is an essential tool in the field of massage therapy, combining form and function to create a peaceful space conducive to healing and relaxation. Every element of the massage table, from its robust construction to its luxurious padding and ergonomic features, contributes significantly to the overall client experience.</p>"	cmqagwxan01aycgtnnwu1jccf	cmq0jhmi20000cgcbtc248zz0	estheticaspafurniture	PUBLISHED	2024-04-19 18:41:13	\N	Comprehensive Guide to the Art & Science of Massage Tables	Discover the art and science behind choosing massage tables. This guide helps spa professionals select quality designs, materials, and ergonomic features.	{"massage tables"}	\N	Comprehensive Guide to the Art & Science of Massage Tables	Discover the art and science behind choosing massage tables. This guide helps spa professionals select quality designs, materials, and ergonomic features.	\N	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 07:15:58.408	2026-06-12 05:19:31.579
cmq0lbhbz04hacgcb3f6s1h3w	Manicure Table At Best Price in India	manicure-table-best-price-india	Manicure Table —a committed workspace wherein nail technicians paint their magic and customers take pleasure in pampering treatments. Esthetica is a relied-on supplier, offering professional manicure tables and nail tables for the spa and salon industry. The Significance of Manicure Tables: The Mani…	"<p class=\\"ai-optimize-introduction ai-optimize-6\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/damini-manicure-table/\\">Manicure Table</a>—a committed workspace wherein nail technicians paint their magic and customers take pleasure in pampering treatments. Esthetica is a relied-on supplier, offering professional manicure tables and nail tables for the spa and salon industry.</p>\\n\\n<h2 class=\\"ai-optimize-7\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>The Significance of Manicure Tables:</strong></h2>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-8\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">The Manicure Table serves as one of the most important pieces of furniture for nail art studios. These specialized tables are designed keeping in mind functionality, hygiene, durability, and guest &amp; nail technicians' comfort in mind.</p>\\n\\n<h2 class=\\"ai-optimize-9\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>Why choose Esthetica's  Manicure Table and Nail Tables :</strong></h2>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-10\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Investing in a nail trimming desk from Esthetica Spa Furniture gives a plethora of blessings, inclusive:</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-11\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>1. Superior Quality:</strong> Each nail filing table is constructed with the usage of top-class raw materials and the latest production techniques, ensuring sturdiness, stability, and longevity.</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-12\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>2. Innovative Designs:</strong> Esthetica gives a wide form of nail station desk designs, ranging from sleek modern-day to classic professional designs, permitting salon proprietors to find the ideal manicure table for their nail studio set-up.</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-13\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>3. Competitive Pricing:</strong> Despite the first-rate high-quality of its products, we offer competitive pricing, making it handy to salons and spas of all sizes and budgets.</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-14\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>4. Customization Options:</strong> Esthetica offers customization options for nail tables, allowing salon proprietors to tailor the design, coloration, and capabilities to their particular possibilities and requirements.</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-15\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>5. Exceptional Customer Service:</strong> Esthetica Spa <a href=\\"https://www.estheticamedicalfurniture.com/\\">Furniture</a> is dedicated to imparting splendid customer support, with a team of experts equipped to assist clients every step of the way, from choice to installation.</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-16\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>6. Nail Dust Extraction System:</strong> Keeping in mind the health of the customers and nail technicians, we offer a powerful nail dust extraction system at our professional tables to collect nail dust and prevent it from being spread in the air.</p>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><img class=\\"wp-image-5155 aligncenter\\" src=\\"/uploads/wp-legacy/2024/05/jhfgjghj-200x150.png\\" alt=\\"Manicure Table\\" width=\\"440\\" height=\\"331\\" /><img class=\\" wp-image-4652 alignleft\\" src=\\"/uploads/wp-legacy/2018/12/Preeti-1-1-200x150.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"331\\" height=\\"248\\" /></p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-17\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>Key Features to Consider When Choosing a <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/preeti-nail-table/\\">Nail Table</a>:</strong></p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-18\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Some key points to consider while choosing your nail table :</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-19\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>1. Spacious Work Surface:</strong> Look for a manicure table with enough area to deal with nail care equipment, systems, and products, allowing technicians to work correctly without feeling cramped.</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-20\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>2. Built-in Storage:</strong> Opt for a manicure table with integrated garage booths, drawers, and shelves to keep nail polish bottles, documents, buffers, and different necessities prepared and inside smoothly attained.</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-21\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>3. Ergonomic Design:</strong> Choose a manicure table with ergonomic functions along with adjustable height settings, padded armrests, and snug seating options to sell technician consolation and reduce fatigue at some stage in lengthy hours of work</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-22\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>4. Sturdy Construction:</strong> Select a manicure table constituted of super materials along with wood, steel, or acrylic, with reinforced joints and strong legs to ensure balance and sturdiness.</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-23\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>5. Easy Maintenance:</strong> Consider a <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/damini-manicure-table/\\">manicure table</a> with a clean and non-porous floor that is simple to easily disinfect. A <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/nalini-nail-table/\\">Nail Dust Collector</a> supports in preserving a hygienic environment.</p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-24\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>Conclusion:</strong></p>\\n<p class=\\"ai-optimize-25\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">In conclusion, investing in a functional and professional manicure table is important for a salon or spa. With <u><a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/manicure-pedicure-chairs/\\">Esthetica</a></u>you may increase your salon experience with nail tables that combine style, functionality, and affordability.</p>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"></p>\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"></p>"	cmqagwxvt01becgtnu7spbf20	cmq0jhmi20000cgcbtc248zz0	estheticaspafurniture	PUBLISHED	2024-05-20 18:40:28	\N	Manicure Table At Best Price in India	Professional Manicure and Nail Tables from Esthetica. Available in basic and pro models with nail dust extraction system and LED Light	{"Manicure Table","Nail Art Table"}	\N	Manicure Table At Best Price in India	Professional Manicure and Nail Tables from Esthetica. Available in basic and pro models with nail dust extraction system and LED Light	\N	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 07:15:58.464	2026-06-12 05:19:31.619
cmq0lbhcn04hucgcb6oa7uhpq	Ultimate Guide to Zero Gravity Chairs: Your Ticket to Blissful Relaxation	guide-zero-gravity-chairs	In today's fast-paced world, finding moments of pure relaxation can feel like a luxury. But what if I told you that you could experience the sensation of weightlessness, relieve tension in your body, and promote spinal health all at once? Enter the Zero Gravity Chair – a marvel of engineering design…	"<strong>In today's fast-paced world, finding moments of pure relaxation can feel like a luxury. But what if I told you that you could experience the sensation of weightlessness, relieve tension in your body, and promote spinal health all at once? Enter the Zero Gravity Chair – a marvel of engineering designed to provide unparalleled comfort and rejuvenation. In this comprehensive guide, we'll explore everything you need to know about Zero Gravity Chairs and why Esthetica's Zero Gravity Chair stands out as the epitome of relaxation.</strong>\\n<h2><a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/zero-gravity-chair/\\"><strong>What is a Zero Gravity Chair?</strong></a></h2>\\nA Zero Gravity Chair represents a pinnacle of relaxation engineering. Crafted with precision and innovation, these specially designed recliners redefine the concept of comfort. Zero Gravity Chairs ingeniously position the body in a reclined posture that minimizes the strain imposed by gravitational forces. This strategic alignment not only alleviates pressure on the spine but also facilitates optimal circulation throughout the body.\\n\\nWhether you seek relief from chronic back pain, desire to enhance your overall well-being, or simply crave a moment of pure tranquility, a Zero Gravity Chair offers an oasis of comfort where stress fades away and bliss takes center stage.\\n\\n<img class=\\"aligncenter wp-image-5168\\" src=\\"/uploads/wp-legacy/2024/05/fdgdg-200x164.png\\" alt=\\"Zero Gravity Chair\\" width=\\"287\\" height=\\"236\\" />\\n\\n<h3><strong>Benefits of Zero Gravity Chairs</strong></h3>\\n<ol>\\n \\t<li><strong>Spinal Health</strong></li>\\n</ol>\\nZero Gravity Chairs are renowned for their ability to promote spinal health. When you recline in a Zero Gravity position, your body is positioned in such a way that the spine is aligned and the pressure on the vertebrae is reduced. This alignment not only relieves strain on the lower back but also helps to decompress the spine.\\n<ol start=\\"2\\">\\n \\t<li><strong>Improved Circulation</strong></li>\\n</ol>\\nThe unique design of Zero Gravity Chairs also promotes better blood flow throughout the body. By elevating the legs slightly above the heart level, these chairs facilitate venous return, which is the process of blood flow back to the heart. This elevation helps to reduce swelling in the lower extremities and enhances overall circulation.\\n\\nImproved circulation has numerous benefits for physical health, including better oxygenation of tissues, improved nutrient delivery, and faster removal of metabolic waste products. Beyond the physical benefits, enhanced circulation also promotes a sense of relaxation and well-being, as the body feels lighter and more energized.\\n<ol>\\n \\t<li><strong>Muscle Tension Relief</strong></li>\\n</ol>\\nWhether you lead a sedentary lifestyle or engage in physically demanding activities, muscle tension is a common issue for many people. Zero-gravity chairs offer effective relief by distributing body weight evenly across the entire body surface. This even distribution of weight helps to reduce pressure points and allows muscles to relax more fully.\\n<h3><strong>Esthetica's Zero Gravity Chair: The Ultimate Relaxation Lounger</strong></h3>\\nAmong the myriad Zero Gravity Chairs available on the market, Esthetica's Zero Gravity Chair stands out as a beacon of comfort and quality. Crafted with precision and attention to detail, this chair is designed to elevate your relaxation experience to new heights.\\n\\n<strong>Promoting Spinal Health:</strong> Esthetica's Zero Gravity Chair is not just a piece of furniture; it's a wellness solution. Built on the principle of neutral body posture, this chair provides unparalleled support for your spine. Gently cradling your body in a Zero Gravity position relieves pressure on the lumbar spine, decompresses spinal discs, and promotes optimal alignment.\\n\\n<strong>Customized Comfort:</strong> When it comes to relaxation, one size does not fit all. That's why Esthetica's Zero Gravity Chair is equipped with dual motors, allowing you to customize your comfort with the touch of a button. Whether you prefer a gentle recline or full zero-gravity immersion, the leg section and backrest can be independently adjusted to suit your needs. Find your perfect position and drift away into a state of pure tranquillity.\\n\\n<strong>Enhanced Spa Experience: </strong>Esthetica's Zero Gravity Chair isn't just for home use – it's also the perfect addition to your spa or wellness centre. Elevate your client's experience with the ultimate relaxation lounger, designed to promote spinal health and rejuvenate the body and mind. Pair it with our Pedicure Trolley with Copper/Brass Bowl for a complete relaxation package that will leave your clients feeling pampered and revitalized.\\n\\n<li>\\n<strong>Experience the Difference with Esthetica's Zero Gravity Chair</strong>\\n</li>\\n\\nAre you ready to experience the ultimate in relaxation and spinal health? Look no further than Esthetica's <a href=\\"https://www.wikipedia.org/\\"><strong>Zero Gravity Chair</strong>.</a> With its innovative design, unparalleled comfort, and myriad health benefits, this chair is a must-have for anyone seeking a moment of pure bliss.\\n\\nOrder yours today and discover why Esthetica's Zero Gravity Chair is the preferred choice for spas, wellness centres, and relaxation enthusiasts worldwide. Visit <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/\\">Esthetica's</a> website to place your order today and take the first step toward a healthier, happier you. Elevate your spa offerings with Esthetica's Zero Gravity Chair and Pedicure Trolley with Copper/Brass Bowl. Visit Esthetica's website to explore our full range of relaxation solutions and take your spa to the next level."	cmqagwxx401bgcgtnx9xbvci2	cmq0jhmi20000cgcbtc248zz0	estheticaspafurniture	PUBLISHED	2024-05-22 16:39:53	\N	Zero Gravity Chairs: The Ultimate Guide to Relaxation	Explore the benefits of Zero Gravity Chairs for spa. Relieve tension, promote spinal health, and experience the sensation of weightlessness.	{"Zero Gravity Chairs for Spa"}	\N	Zero Gravity Chairs: The Ultimate Guide to Relaxation	Explore the benefits of Zero Gravity Chairs for spa. Relieve tension, promote spinal health, and experience the sensation of weightlessness.	\N	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 07:15:58.487	2026-06-12 05:19:31.638
