cmq0jhmjy000pcgcbfms4hpz1	Spa Trolleys	spa-trolleys	<h1>Elevate Your Spa Experience with Esthetica’s Spa Trolleys</h1><p>At Esthetica, we understand that spa trolleys are an integral part of any spa room setup. These versatile <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-carts/"><strong>spa carts</strong></a> allow you to effortlessly move essential supplies around during treatments, keeping your spa oils, creams, and towels within easy reach for a seamless massage experience.</p><p>Our diverse range of spa trolleys is designed to meet various needs, ensuring that you find the perfect solution for your treatment space. Choose from low-height pedicure trolleys, barber trolleys, and specialized equipment trolleys, as well as carts specifically designed for hot towel cabinets, laser machines, and massage stone heaters.</p><p>Crafted from high-quality materials, our spa trolleys are mostly made in solid wood, however, some designs use mild steel and elegant glass shelves. Most of these spa treatment room trolleys are equipped with three-tier storage but you will also find designs in our portfolio with drawer cabinets, providing ample storage for all your spa essentials.</p><p>Customization is at the heart of our offerings. We invite you to personalize your spa trolley to match your spa treatment bed or spa room’s aesthetics. Select your desired size and finishes to create a cohesive and inviting atmosphere that reflects your brand.</p><p>With Esthetica’s spa trolleys, you can enhance the efficiency and organization of your <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.portablemassagebed.in/"><strong>spa treatments</strong></a> while elevating the overall experience for your clients. Explore our collection today and discover how our expertly de</p><h2>Esthetica’s Global Presence</h2><p>Esthetica Spa &amp; Salon Resources Pvt Ltd has established a formidable global presence as a leading manufacturer and exporter of premium quality spa treatment room trolleys. Our spa carts are highly sought after, with <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/international-distributors/"><strong>international distribution</strong></a> spanning countries such as the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/"><strong>UAE</strong></a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/qatar/"><strong>Qatar</strong></a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/saudi-arabia/"><strong>Saudi Arabia</strong></a>, Oman, Bahrain, Belgium, the United Kingdom, Australia, South Africa, Poland, and the USA, among others in Asia and Europe. Committed to excellence, we ensure our high-quality offerings reach clients worldwide, facilitated by preferential trade agreements that allow for duty-free exports to Australia, the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/"><strong>UAE</strong></a>, and ASEAN countries. This strategic approach not only enhances our competitiveness but also solidifies our reputation as a trusted partner in the wellness industry on a global scale</p>	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "Keep your essential tools and products organized and within reach with our stylish and functional spa trolleys. Massage oils, towels, everything moves effortlessly.", "type": "text"}]}]}	\N	cmq0jhmjv000ncgcbemmh3o9w	6	t	PUBLISHED	en-IN	2026-06-19 12:22:50.056	Buy Premium Spa Trolleys & Carts Online – Esthetica	Buy premium spa trolleys for organized and efficient service. Spa cart options with wheels and storage. Perfect for salons, spas, and wellness centers. Visit now!	{"Spa Trolleys",trolley,Pedicure,"Salon Cart","barber trolley"}	https://spa.acnosoft.com/spa-trolleys/	Buy Premium Spa Trolleys & Carts Online – Esthetica	Buy