cmq0jhmjm000mcgcb25d0lglp	Spa Stools	spa-stools	<h1>Discover Our Exquisite Range of Spa Stools</h1><p>At Esthetica, we offer a carefully curated selection of spa stools that blend functionality and style to enhance your treatment spaces. Our product range includes a variety of handcrafted solid wood spa stools, perfect for indoor use in treatment rooms. These durable and elegant stools add a touch of sophistication to any spa environment.</p><p>For therapists on the go, our easy-to-carry folding therapist stools provide a practical solution without compromising comfort. Additionally, our low-height pedicurist chairs and stools are specifically designed for manicure and pedicure areas, ensuring that your clients enjoy a comfortable experience while you work.</p><p>Our designer spa therapist chairs feature stylish wooden backrests, combining aesthetics with ergonomic support. For medical and beauty treatment rooms, we offer stools crafted with aluminum alloy bases and stainless steel components, ensuring durability and ease of maintenance.</p><p>Most of our wooden stools are fixed-height, providing stability, while our other designs come equipped with gas lifts for height adjustment and castor wheels for effortless mobility around the treatment room. This versatility allows you to tailor your workspace to meet the needs of each client and service.</p><p>Customization is key at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.estheticamedicalfurniture.com/"><strong>Esthetica</strong></a>. The upholstery of our attendant chairs can be personalized to match your massage or treatment table upholstery, creating a cohesive and visually appealing environment that enhances the overall experience for your clients.</p><p>Transform your spa or treatment room with our premium spa stools, designed for comfort, functionality, and style. Explore our collection today and discover the perfect seating solutions to elevate your service offerings!</p><h2>Esthetica’