cmq0jv6zj0019cgcbcbzn7tl3	Massage Tables	massage-beds	<h1>Welcome to Esthetica: Your Premier Destination for Massage Beds</h1><p>At Esthetica, we specialize in the art of crafting high-quality massage beds designed to enhance the comfort and functionality of any spa, salon, wellness centre, or private practice. Our extensive range includes everything from premium electric spa massage tables to wooden massage beds with storage, ensuring we have the perfect solution for every therapist's needs.</p><p></p><h2>Our Diverse Range of Massage Beds</h2><ul><li><p><strong>Premium Electric Spa Massage Tables</strong>:<br>Our&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/products/electric-spa-bed-marut/">electric spa massage tables</a>&nbsp;are engineered for versatility and ease of use. With adjustable heights and settings, these tables provide therapists with the ability to cater to each client's unique preferences. The smooth electric operation allows for seamless transitions between treatments, enhancing the overall experience for both the therapist and the client.</p></li><li><p><strong>Wooden Massage Beds with Storage</strong>:<br>For those looking for a touch of elegance combined with practicality, our wooden massage beds with storage are ideal. Crafted from high-quality materials, these beds not only provide a stable and luxurious surface for treatments but also offer integrated storage solutions, ensuring your workspace remains organized and clutter-free.</p></li><li><p><strong>Low-Height Thai Massage Beds</strong>:<br>Our low-height Thai massage beds are specifically designed to accommodate traditional Thai massage techniques. These beds allow for easy access and mobility, promoting a more effective and authentic massage experience.</p></li><li><p><strong>Ayurvedic Massage Beds</strong>:<br>Embrace the healing traditions of Ayurveda with our specialized&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/products/ayurveda-table/">Ayurvedic massage beds</a>. These beds are thoughtfully designed to support various Ayurvedic treatments, offering both comfort and functionality for holistic practitioners.</p></li><li><p><strong>Portable Massage Tables</strong>:<br>For therapists on the go, our&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.portablemassagebed.in/">portable massage tables</a>&nbsp;offer convenience without compromising on quality. Lightweight yet sturdy, these tables can be easily transported, making them perfect for home visits, outdoor events, or temporary setups.</p></li><li><p><strong>Massage Tables for Reiki</strong>:<br>Our massage tables for Reiki are tailored to provide a serene and supportive environment for energy healing practices. These tables feature comfortable padding and adjustable settings to enhance the Reiki experience.</p></li><li><p><strong>Prenatal Massage Tables</strong>:<br>We understand the importance of comfort during pregnancy. Our prenatal massage tables are designed with special features to support expectant mothers, providing them with a safe and comfortable space for relaxation and therapeutic care.</p></li></ul><h3>Customization Options</h3><p></p><p>At Esthetica, we believe that each therapist has unique needs. That’s why we offer extensive customization options. You can choose the size, wood stain colour, and upholstery colour of your massage bed to create a piece that perfectly aligns with your aesthetic and functional requirements. High-Quality Materials and Craftsmanship All our massage beds are manufactured using real wood or real wood veneers, ensuring durability and a premium look. Our skilled craftsmen employ proper carpentry techniques, including tenon and mortise joinery, to guarantee the strength and stability required in any professional setting. We take pride in our meticulous attention to detail and precision, ensuring that each piece is built to last.</p><h3>Comfort Features</h3><p><strong>Premium Cushioning</strong> Comfort is paramount in any massage setting. Our beds are equipped with premium cushioning, combining high-resilience foam with latex and memory foam for an optimal experience. This unique blend not only provides support but also adapts to the contours of the body, ensuring maximum comfort for clients during treatments. <strong>Adjustable Armrests</strong> Our massage beds come with lower-able armrests that provide added convenience and comfort. These armrests can be adjusted according to the treatment being provided, ensuring that clients are fully supported throughout their sessions. <strong>In-Built Heating Function</strong> Enhance your clients’ relaxation with our&nbsp;built-in&nbsp;heating function. This feature provides gentle warmth that helps to soothe muscles and promote a deeper level of relaxation, creating an unforgettable experience.</p><h3>Eco-Friendly Options</h3><p>At Esthetica, we are committed to sustainability. We offer a variety of eco-friendly options, including:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Eco-Friendly Recycled Leather:</strong>&nbsp;Our premium upholstery options include eco-friendly recycled leather, helping to protect the environment while maintaining the luxurious feel of your massage bed.</p></li><li><p><strong>Water-Based Coatings:</strong>&nbsp;Choose from our eco-friendly water-based coatings or opt for standard solvent-based polyurethane coatings to finish your massage bed. Both options are designed to enhance durability while being conscious of environmental impact.</p></li></ul><h3>Collaborate with Us</h3><p>Let us help you find the perfect massage bed tailored to your specific needs. We invite you to collaborate with us; and share your requirements, and our expert team will provide personalized recommendations to suggest the most suitable table for your practice. Whether you are setting up a new spa or upgrading your existing equipment, Esthetica is here to support you every step of the way.</p><h3>Why Choose Esthetica?</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Quality Assurance:</strong>&nbsp;We prioritize quality in every aspect of our manufacturing process, ensuring you receive a product that meets the highest standards.</p></li><li><p><strong>Expertise:</strong>&nbsp;With years of experience in crafting massage beds, our knowledgeable team understands the nuances of what makes a table exceptional.</p></li><li><p><strong>Customer Satisfaction:</strong>&nbsp;Our commitment to customer satisfaction means we are always ready to listen and adapt to your needs.</p></li></ul><h3>Esthetica’s Global Presence</h3><p>Esthetica Spa &amp; Salon Resources Pvt Ltd has established a formidable global presence as a leading manufacturer and exporter of premium quality massage tables. Our products are highly sought after, with&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/international-distributors/">international distribution</a>&nbsp;spanning countries such as the&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/">UAE</a>,&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/qatar/">Qatar</a>,&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/saudi-arabia/">Saudi Arabia</a>, Oman, Bahrain, Belgium, the United Kingdom, Australia, South Africa, Poland, and the USA, among others in Asia and Europe. Committed to excellence, we ensure our high-quality offerings reach clients worldwide, facilitated by preferential trade agreements that allow for duty-free exports to Australia, the&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/">UAE</a>, and ASEAN countries. This strategic approach not only enhances our competitiveness but also solidifies our reputation as a trusted partner in the wellness industry on a global scale</p><h3>Conclusion</h3><p>Transform your massage practice with our premium range of massage beds at Esthetica. From electric spa tables to portable options, each bed is crafted with precision and care, ensuring the best experience for therapists and clients. With extensive customization options and a commitment to eco-friendly practices, Esthetica is your trusted partner in wellness. Contact us today to discuss your requirements, and let’s create the perfect massage bed for you!</p>	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}	\N	cmqalsrtq0005cgci8ryim8k5	1	t	PUBLISHED	en-IN	2026-06-26 05:54:31.562	Buy Spa Massage Beds Online | High-Quality Spa Treatment Beds	Shop premium spa massage beds and spa beds online at Esthetica. Discover high-quality, ergonomic massage beds designed for comfort, style, and durability.	{"Massage Beds"}	https://spa.acnosoft.com/massage-tables/	Massage Beds: Enhancing Comfort and Functionality at Esthetica	Find the ideal massage beds for your wellness center or private practice at Esthetica. Explore our premium electric spa massage tables and more.	cmqalsrtq0005cgci8ryim8k5	summary_large_image	null	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 06:35:18.918	2026-06-26 05:54:31.567	<p>Massage beds are the centre of any treatment room. Premium hardwood, comfy cushioning, and adjustable settings make our massage beds a cut above the rest. Massages, facials, and Ayurvedic treatments all benefit from using these. As experienced massage table manufacturers, we offer a range of designs, from Electric to stationary wooden models, as per your operational needs.</p>	cmqalrr6z0001cgcifuyy7jsm	t	0	\N
cmq0jv6zx001dcgcbt0w666r5	Loungers	spa-relaxation-loungers	<h1>Welcome to Esthetica: Your Destination for Premium Relaxation Beds</h1><p>At Esthetica, we believe that relaxation should be a luxurious experience, whether indoors or outdoors. Our exquisite range of relaxation beds is designed to elevate any space, combining functionality, comfort, and style. Crafted from the finest materials and designed with meticulous attention to detail, our beds are perfect for both residential and commercial settings, including hotels and resorts.</p><h3>Outdoor Poolside Loungers</h3><p>Transform your outdoor space with our premium quality relaxation beds, specifically designed for poolside areas. Our loungers are expertly crafted from solid teak wood using traditional tenon and mortise joinery, ensuring exceptional durability and stability. Each piece is finished with marine-grade wood adhesives and treated with Italian outdoor wood coatings, making them resilient against the harshest weather conditions.</p><h3>Superior Outdoor Upholstery</h3><p>Our commitment to quality extends beyond the wood. We utilize premium outdoor upholstery featuring a Nano high-tech compound that enhances longevity and ease of maintenance. This fabric is:</p><ul><li><p><strong>UV Resistant:</strong>&nbsp;Protects against sun damage and fading.</p></li><li><p><strong>Oil Resistant:</strong>&nbsp;Easy to clean and maintain.</p></li><li><p><strong>Weather Resistant:</strong>&nbsp;Stands up to rain and humidity.</p></li><li><p><strong>Disinfectant Resistant:</strong>&nbsp;Suitable for high-traffic areas and ensures hygiene.</p></li><li><p><strong>Salt Water and Chlorine Resistant:</strong>&nbsp;Perfect for poolside environments.</p></li></ul><p>With these features, our loungers are not only comfortable but also practical for any outdoor setting.</p><h3>Indoor Spa Loungers</h3><p>In addition to our outdoor offerings, Esthetica provides a stunning collection of indoor spa loungers, available in both electric and non-electric models. Our indoor loungers are designed to provide optimal comfort, making them ideal for spa settings, wellness centres, or relaxation areas in hotels.</p><h2>Electric Spa Relaxation Loungers</h2><p>Our powered spa loungers take relaxation to the next level with advanced features designed for ultimate convenience:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Electronic Backrest and Leg Rest Adjustments:</strong>&nbsp;Customize your position for maximum comfort.</p></li><li><p><strong>Detachable Reading Lamp:</strong>&nbsp;Enjoy your favourite book or magazine while you relax.</p></li><li><p><strong>USB Charging Socket:</strong>&nbsp;Stay connected even while you unwind.</p></li><li><p><strong>In-built Heating Function:</strong>&nbsp;Add an extra layer of comfort with adjustable warmth.</p></li><li><p><strong>Foldable Lateral Shelf Support:</strong>&nbsp;Convenient for personal items or refreshments.</p></li></ul><p>These electric loungers are perfect for creating a luxurious spa experience, ensuring your clients can fully unwind and indulge in relaxation.</p><h3>Non-Electric Spa Relaxation Beds</h3><p>For those who prefer a more traditional approach, our non-electric relaxation beds are ergonomically designed for maximum comfort. These versatile beds can be used indoors or in wet areas, offering a seamless blend of functionality and style. The ergonomic design, combined with comfortable upholstery and foam cushioning, ensures that every client enjoys a restorative experience.</p><h3>Customization for Your Unique Space</h3><p>At Esthetica, we understand that every space is unique. As a factory producing these spa loungers, we offer customization options to meet your specific needs. You can personalize the following aspects:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Size:</strong>&nbsp;Tailor the dimensions to fit your space perfectly.</p></li><li><p><strong>Wood Finish:</strong>&nbsp;Choose from a variety of finishes to match your decor.</p></li><li><p><strong>Upholstery Colour:</strong>&nbsp;Select the ideal colour to complement your design scheme.</p></li></ul><p>With our custom options, you can create relaxation beds that are not only functional but also enhance the aesthetic of your spa or resort.</p><h3>Why Choose Esthetica?</h3><p>When you choose Esthetica, you are choosing quality, craftsmanship, and innovation. Our dedication to using the finest materials and advanced technology sets us apart from the competition. We strive to ensure that every relaxation bed we produce meets the highest standards, allowing you to offer an unparalleled experience to your clients.</p><h3>Exceptional Customer Support</h3><p>Our commitment to customer satisfaction doesn’t end with your purchase. We provide exceptional customer support to assist you in selecting the right products and addressing any questions or concerns you may have. Our knowledgeable team is always here to help you create the perfect relaxation environment.</p><h3>Elevate Your Space Today</h3><p>Enhance your indoor and outdoor relaxation areas with Esthetica’s premium relaxation beds. Explore our collection and discover the perfect loungers to complement your <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.portablemassagebed.in/"><strong>spa</strong></a> or resort. Contact us today to learn more about our products and customization options, and let us help you create a haven of relaxation for your clients. Choose Esthetica for an unmatched blend of luxury and functionality!</p><h3>Esthetica’s Global Presence</h3><p>Esthetica Spa &amp; Salon Resources Pvt Ltd has installed its spa relaxation loungers in many premium spa resorts and hotels,&nbsp;spas across the globe. The Bodhi Spa in the USA and Wai Araki in New Zealand are using <strong>Mandakani Spa Relaxation Loungers</strong>. &nbsp;Our products are highly sought after, with <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/international-distributors/"><strong>international distribution</strong></a> spanning countries such as the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/"><strong>UAE</strong></a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/qatar/"><strong>Qatar</strong></a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/saudi-arabia/"><strong>Saudi Arabia</strong></a>, Oman, Bahrain, Belgium, the United Kingdom, Australia, South Africa, Poland, and the USA, among others in Asia and Europe. Committed to excellence, we ensure our high-quality offerings reach clients worldwide, facilitated by preferential trade agreements that allow for duty-free exports to Australia, the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/"><strong>UAE</strong></a>, and ASEAN countries. This strategic approach not only enhances our competitiveness but also solidifies our reputation as a trusted partner in the wellness industry on a global scale.</p>	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "Create serene relaxation areas with our elegant loungers. Unwind before and after treatments on these comfortably designed ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "loungers", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "href": "https://www.spafurniture.in/products/loungers/", "class": null, "title": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": ". You’ll feel weightless and stress-free – pure bliss!", "type": "text"}]}]}	\N	cmq0y8q72000ccg46bvtlkmbh	2	t	PUBLISHED	en-IN	2026-06-29 07:14:27.455	Buy Spa Relaxation Beds with Cushioned Loungers – Esthetica	Buy spa relaxation beds designed for ultimate comfort. Explore cushioned loungers ideal for spas, wellness centers, and luxury retreats. Shop Esthetica now	{"Spa Relaxation Lounger",Loungers,"Relaxation Loungers","Poolside Lounge",Lounger}	https://spa.acnosoft.com/loungers/	Spa Relaxation Bed 