cmq0jv700001ecgcb1wacenz3	Salon Furniture	salon-furniture	<h1>Discover Premium Salon Furniture at Esthetica</h1><p>Welcome to Esthetica, where we elevate your spa and salon experience with our exceptional range of premium salon furniture. We recognize that every hotel spa, home spa, or resort spa features a dedicated area for salon services, and the quality of your furniture can make all the difference. That’s why we offer a curated selection of high-quality salon chairs, styling chairs, barber chairs, and make-up chairs designed to blend comfort, functionality, and aesthetic appeal.</p><h3>Tailored Solutions for Every Space</h3><p>Our salon furniture collection is crafted to meet the diverse needs of the salon industry. Whether you’re operating a bustling hotel spa or a serene home salon, we have the perfect solutions for your space. Our offerings include:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Salon Chairs:</strong>&nbsp;Designed with ergonomics in mind, our salon chairs provide the comfort and support your clients deserve, ensuring a delightful experience from the moment they sit down.</p></li><li><p><strong>Styling Chairs:</strong>&nbsp;Our styling chairs combine elegance and practicality, making them ideal for all hair types and styling needs. With adjustable features, they cater to the comfort of both stylists and clients.</p></li><li><p><strong>Barber Chairs:</strong>&nbsp;Built to provide durability and comfort, our barber chairs are designed for traditional barbering as well as modern styling techniques, ensuring versatility in your services.</p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.estheticamedicalfurniture.com/"><strong>Make-Up Chairs</strong></a><strong>:</strong>&nbsp;Enhance your make-up application services with our specialized chairs that offer support and style, creating an inviting space for your clients.</p></li></ul><h3></h3><h2>Innovative Hair Wash and Shampoo Stations</h2><p>One of our standout offerings is our high-end hair wash stations and shampoo stations, which are designed to provide an indulgent experience for your clients. These stations come equipped with:</p><ul><li><p><strong>In-built Massage Functions:</strong>&nbsp;Add a touch of luxury with massage features that promote relaxation and elevate the shampoo experience.</p></li><li><p><strong>Electric Leg Raise Function:</strong>&nbsp;Enhance comfort for your clients with adjustable leg support, making every visit a pampering session.</p></li></ul><h3></h3><h3>Customization for a Cohesive Look</h3><p>At Esthetica, we understand the importance of aesthetics in creating a harmonious atmosphere. That’s why we offer customization options for upholstery to match the décor of your spa furniture, ensuring a seamless and unified look throughout your space.</p><h3>Branding Opportunities</h3><p>To further enhance your branding, we provide the option to emboss your logo on the upholstery of your salon furniture. This not only adds a personal touch but also reinforces your brand identity, creating a lasting impression on your clients.</p><h3>Comprehensive Salon Equipment</h3><p>In addition to our luxurious salon furniture, Esthetica is proud to offer a wide range of salon equipment to complete your setup:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Barber Trolleys:</strong>&nbsp;Keep your workspace organized with our functional and stylish barber trolleys, designed for easy access to tools.</p></li><li><p><strong>Facial Trolleys:</strong>&nbsp;Our facial trolleys are perfect for aestheticians, equipped to hold all your essential products and tools for a streamlined workflow.</p></li><li><p><strong>Hair Trolleys:</strong>&nbsp;Ensure efficiency during hair services with our versatile hair trolleys, designed to keep your tools within reach.</p></li><li><p><strong>Hair Dryers &amp; Irons:</strong>&nbsp;Our high-quality hair dryers and styling irons ensure that your clients leave looking their best.</p></li><li><p><strong>Facial Steamers:</strong>&nbsp;Enhance your facial treatments with our professional-grade facial steamers, designed for effective and relaxing sessions.</p></li><li><p><strong>UV Instrument Sterilizers:</strong>&nbsp;Maintain the highest hygiene standards in your salon with our UV sterilizers, essential for client safety.</p></li></ul><h3></h3><h3>Elevate Your Salon Experience</h3><p>At Esthetica, we are dedicated to providing you with the best in salon furniture and equipment. Our commitment to quality, customization, and customer satisfaction sets us apart as your go-to source for all your salon needs. Explore our range today and transform your salon into a haven of comfort and style, ensuring your clients always leave feeling rejuvenated and pampered.</p><h3>Esthetica’s Global Presence</h3><p>Esthetica Spa &amp; Salon Resources Pvt Ltd has established a formidable global presence as a leading manufacturer and exporter of premium quality salon chairs and hair wash units. Our products are highly sought after, with <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/international-distributors/"><strong>international distribution</strong></a> spanning countries such as the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/"><strong>UAE</strong></a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/qatar/"><strong>Qatar</strong></a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/saudi-arabia/"><strong>Saudi Arabia</strong></a>, Oman, Bahrain, Belgium, the United Kingdom, Australia, South Africa, Poland, and the USA, among others in Asia and Europe. Committed to excellence, we ensure our high-quality offerings reach clients worldwide, facilitated by preferential trade agreements that allow for duty-free exports to Australia, the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/"><strong>UAE</strong></a>, and ASEAN countries. This strategic approach not only enhances our competitiveness but also solidifies our reputation as a trusted partner in the wellness industry on a global scale.</p>	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}	\N	cmq0y9ojk000kcg46fkfe9kgp	4	t	PUBLISHED	en-IN	2026-06-19 07:55:55.286	Explore Premium Salon Furniture & Chairs Online At Esthetica	Buy salon & barber chairs, hair styling chairs, and makeup chairs crafted for elegance and comfort. Perfect for salons, studios, and beauty professionals.	{"Salon Furniture","Barber Chair","Salon Chair","Salon Furniture Supplier","shampoo chair"}	https://spa.acnosoft.com/salon-furniture/	Salon Furniture: Barber, Styling, Shampoo, & Salon Chairs	Find the perfect salon furniture for hotels, home spas, or resorts. Quality designs that blend beauty and functionality.	cmq0y9ojk000kcg46fkfe9kgp	summary_large_image	null	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 06:35:18.96	2026-06-19 12:25:26.214	<p>Our salon furniture products include styling chairs, shampoo stations, and treatment beds. Your salon will be more efficient and stylish with our products.</p>	cmqao7sn1000tcggdqmxjhsvc	t	3	\N
