cmqtd8f6v000icgolvr35olff	COSMOPROF BOLOGNA 2027*	2026-06-26 16:04:00	cmquludes000fcgiefe8jmecb	\N	PUBLISHED	2026-06-29 05:23:20.231	2026-06-25 10:34:57.895	2026-06-29 05:23:20.232	<img src="/uploads/1782710595533-kzj2d9mmlj9.webp" alt="COSMOPROF-BOLOGNA-2027.jpeg"><p>Esthetica Spa &amp; Salon Furniture will be exhibiting at Cosmoprof Bologna 2027!</p><p>Europe's most prestigious beauty and wellness exhibition, Cosmoprof Bologna returns in 2027, hosting over 3,000+ international exhibitors and attracting more than 250,000+ beauty professionals, salon owners, spa consultants, and procurement managers from across Europe and beyond.</p><p>Cosmoprof Bologna is the world's leading platform for spa and salon innovation — where the finest furniture makers, wellness brands, and beauty technology companies showcase to an elite audience of luxury spa operators, five-star hotel groups, and international salon chains.</p><p>You'll find Esthetica Spa &amp; Salon Furniture at our booth, where we will be presenting our premium range of electric spa treatment tables, relaxation loungers, massage beds, vibroacoustic wellness furniture, pedicure chairs, and bespoke spa solutions — engineered with Italian precision, sustainable materials, and the comfort standards expected by Europe's most discerning wellness facilities.</p><p>We look forward to welcoming you to our stand!</p><p><em>March 2027 (dates to confirm)</em></p><p><em>Hall 30 | Booth F59</em></p><p><em>Cosmoprof Bologna 2027</em></p><p><em>Bolognafiere</em></p><p><em>Bologna, Italy</em></p><p>If you'd like to arrange an appointment, schedule a product demonstration, or discuss bespoke solutions at our booth, please contact us!</p>	Find Us	Come and find Esthetica at a selection of upcoming, shows, events and exhibitions!	Get in Touch!	Call and speak to our sales team today!	+91 98731 44051	tel:+919873144051
cmqtd987y000jcgolb5f73mjx	COSMOPROF ASIA HONG KONG 2026*	2026-06-27 16:05:00	cmqulv2wf000jcgie3s9dj0ww	\N	PUBLISHED	2026-06-29 05:17:42.839	2026-06-25 10:35:35.519	2026-06-29 05:17:42.842	<img src="/uploads/1782709707402-is4knxg8mk.webp" alt="Cosmoprof-Asia-Hong-Kong.jpeg"><p>Esthetica Spa &amp; Salon Furniture will be exhibiting at Cosmoprof Asia Hong Kong 2026!</p><p>Asia's largest beauty and wellness trade show returns to Hong Kong, bringing together over 2,500+ beauty professionals, spa operators, salon owners, and procurement decision-makers from across Asia-Pacific.</p><p>Cosmoprof Asia Hong Kong is the premier gathering for spa and salon furniture, wellness equipment, and beauty innovation — connecting exhibitors directly with luxury spa consultants, hotel procurement teams, and wellness facility managers throughout the region.</p><p>You'll find Esthetica Spa &amp; Salon Furniture at our booth, where we will be showcasing our complete range of electric spa treatment tables, relaxation loungers, massage beds, pedicure chairs, and specialised spa furniture — all crafted with premium Italian engineering, natural American Oak, and Veridura phthalate-free upholstery.</p><p>We look forward to welcoming you to our stand!</p><p><em>November 2026</em></p><p><em>Hall 3E &amp; Concourse | Booth 3E-L2D</em></p><p><em>Cosmoprof Asia Hong Kong 2026</em></p><p><em>Hong Kong Convention and Exhibition Centre</em></p><p><em>Hong Kong</em></p><p>If you'd like to arrange an appointment or schedule a product demonstration at our booth, please contact us!</p>	Find Us	Come and find Esthetica at a selection of upcoming, shows, events and exhibitions!	Get in Touch!	Call and speak to our sales team today!	+91 98731 44051	tel:+919873144051
