COPY public."Faq" (id, "entityType", "entityId", "faqGroupId", question, answer, "sortOrder", "schemaEnabled", "createdAt", "updatedAt") FROM stdin;
cmqkwjdm70002cg08xp7a1mfz	HOMEPAGE	home	\N	Can Esthetica furniture be customized to match our spa's design concept?	Yes. All Esthetica products are available in a wide range of upholstery colours, base finishes, wood veneers, and fabric options. Custom dimensions and bespoke configurations are available on request.	0	t	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191
cmqkwjdm70003cg08cd84wsaq	HOMEPAGE	home	\N	Are your products suitable for five-star hotel and resort spas?	Esthetica furniture is supplied to leading luxury hospitality brands including Six Senses, Raffles, Four Seasons, and Shangri-La. All products are designed to meet the operational and aesthetic demands of high-volume professional environments.	1	t	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191
cmqkwjdm70004cg088s95b3r6	HOMEPAGE	home	\N	Where is Esthetica furniture manufactured?	All products are manufactured at our 34,000 sq. ft. facility in IMT Manesar, Gurgaon, India, using machinery sourced from Italy, Germany, and Taiwan.	2	t	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191
cmqkwjdm70005cg08bill4ara	HOMEPAGE	home	\N	How can I become an authorized Esthetica distributor?	We welcome enquiries from established distributors in markets where we are currently expanding. Please contact us with details of your company and territory.	3	t	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191
cmqkwjdm70006cg08dyt962ng	HOMEPAGE	home	\N	Can I visit the Esthetica facility before placing an order?	Yes. We welcome visits to our manufacturing facility and showroom in IMT Manesar, Gurgaon. Please contact us to schedule an appointment.\n\n	4	t	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191
cmqkwjdm70007cg0851jenuyx	HOMEPAGE	home	\N	What warranty do Esthetica products carry?	Every Esthetica product is backed by a comprehensive manufacturer’s warranty: 1 year on upholstery and heating elements, 3 years on motors and electronic controls, and 5 years on the internal frame structure. All warranty claims are handled directly by our team at our manufacturing facility in IMT Manesar, Gurgaon.	5	t	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191
cmqkwjdm70008cg0880inpe4x	HOMEPAGE	home	\N	What sets Esthetica's craftsmanship apart?	Every Esthetica product is built using real wood and real wood veneer — never laminates or synthetic substitutes. Structural components are precision CNC-machined, and all upholstery is hand-finished in-house by our skilled craftsmen. The result is furniture that combines manufacturing precision with genuine handcraft, built to perform in the world’s most demanding luxury spa environments.\n\n	6	t	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191
cmqkwjdm70009cg08kp63f57u	HOMEPAGE	home	\N	Do you ship internationally?	Yes. Esthetica ships worldwide with an established distributor network across the UK, UAE, Australia, Germany, Belgium, and the USA.\n\n	7	t	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191
cmqkwjdm7000acg08425r3w4k	HOMEPAGE	home	\N	What is the typical lead time for an order?	Lead times vary by product and order volume. Standard lead time is 4–5 weeks. Custom orders may require additional time. Contact us for a confirmed timeline at the time of enquiry.\n\n	8	t	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191
cmqkwjdm7000bcg08so5hkmka	HOMEPAGE	home	\N	What is Esthetica’s approach to sustainability?	Our commitment to sustainability is built into every stage of production. We use real wood and real wood veneer exclusively — no PVC laminates or plastic substitutes. All wood coatings are low-VOC, reducing harmful emissions during manufacturing and throughout the product’s life. Our upholstery materials are plasticiser and phthalate-free, ensuring they are safe for clients, therapists, and the environment. Packaging is plastic-free — all products are shipped in cardboard and wood packaging only.	9	t	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191	2026-06-19 12:25:26.191
