cmq0lbiwb059tcgcb7g3f2uh3	Home	premium-spa-furniture-for-spa-wellness-centres	DEFAULT	"[vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row_content\\" full_height=\\"yes\\" equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"proRotate home-page-graphic-for-nov\\"][vc_column el_class=\\"vertMid\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"none\\" css=\\"\\"]<img class=\\"image-responsive aligncenter wp-image-5829 size-large\\" src=\\"/uploads/wp-legacy/2024/12/moble-alligned-1024x725.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"900\\" height=\\"637\\" />\\n\\n<img class=\\"image-desktop aligncenter wp-image-5818 size-medium\\" src=\\"/uploads/1781241048691-515ezgyhubg.png\\" alt=\\"spa-main\\" width=\\"3508\\" height=\\"2582\\" />[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" el_class=\\"proText\\"]\\n<h6>Featured Here <strong>The Shirodhara Massage Bed</strong></h6>\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row\\" parallax=\\"content-moving\\" parallax_image=\\"1439\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"callAction\\"][vc_column el_class=\\"callBtn\\"][no_simple_title title=\\"Combining design innovation with aesthetics to redefine the standards of spa and wellness furniture. Our spa furniture adheres to the highest international quality standards, reflecting our unwavering commitment to delivering top-tier products.\\" title_font_size=\\"\\" undeline=\\"no_underliner\\" title_align=\\"align_center\\"][wolfe_button text_button=\\"OUR BACKGROUND\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/about-us/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"headingSec\\"][vc_column width=\\"1/3\\" el_class=\\"headingLeft\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2>OUR PRODUCTS</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"text-align: left; font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718;\\">Crafted till Perfection</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\\"2/3\\" el_class=\\"headingDesc\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\"]Explore our extensive collection, featuring high-end electric massage beds, specialized Spa Beds, Hydraulic Massage Tables, Spa Treatment Tables,  <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/ayurveda-table/\\">Ayurvedic Massage Tables</a>, Spa Trolleys, Spa Stools, Relaxation Loungers, Ayurveda Panchakarma Table, Shirodhara &amp; Abhyanga Table, Foot Reflexology Chairs, Manicure Tables, and Luxury Pedicure Chairs. Each piece is meticulously crafted to enhance the ambience and functionality of your spa.<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">As one of the leading </span>spa furniture manufacturers<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">, </span>massage table manufacturers<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">, and </span>massage bed suppliers<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> in India, we offer customizable </span>luxury spa furniture<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> solutions that redefine the standards of comfort and design in modern </span>spa furniture<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"productC\\"][vc_column][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-header\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg1\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"4731\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#massage-beds\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft productCat vMiddle\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h1 style=\\"text-align: center;\\">Massage Beds</h1>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\\">Massage beds are the centre of any treatment room. Premium hardwood, comfy cushioning, and adjustable settings make our <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/electric-spa-bed-marut/\\">massage beds</a> a cut above the rest. Massages, facials, and Ayurvedic treatments all benefit from using these. As experienced massage table manufacturers, we offer a range of designs, from Electric to stationary wooden models, as per your operational needs.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/massage-beds/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-header\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft productCat vMiddle\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: capitalize;\\">Spa Stools</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Spa stools are a versatile addition to any wellness setting. Our <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-stools/\\">spa stools</a> are compact, portable, and comfortable, supporting therapists during long working hours. You can adjust their height, and they roll easily between rooms.</span></p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-stools/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg3\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"1537\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#spa-stools\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-header\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg2\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"1970\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#spa-trolleys\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle headingLeft productCat\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: capitalize;\\">Spa Trolleys</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Keep your essential tools and products organized and within reach with our stylish and functional <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-trolleys/\\">spa trolleys</a>. Massage oils, towels, everything moves effortlessly.</span></p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-trolleys/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-header\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft productCat vMiddle\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: capitalize;\\">Pedicure &amp; Manicure</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\\">Create a relaxing nail care experience with our comfortably designed <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/pedicure-manicure/\\">pedicure and manicure</a> setups. Easy to clean, these units prioritize both client comfort and technician efficiency. Hygiene is a breeze!</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/pedicure-manicure/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg5\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"4703\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#pedicure-manicure\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-header\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg7\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"2685\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#loungers\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft productCat vMiddle\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: capitalize;\\">Loungers</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\\">Create serene relaxation areas with our elegant loungers. Unwind before and after treatments on these comfortably designed <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/loungers/\\">loungers</a>. You'll feel weightless and stress-free – pure bliss!</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-relaxation-loungers/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-header\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle headingLeft productCat\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: capitalize;\\">Salon Furniture</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\\">Our salon furniture products include styling chairs, shampoo stations, and treatment beds. Your salon will be more efficient and stylish with our products.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/salon-furniture/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg4\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"6345\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#salon-furniture\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-header\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg6\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"3941\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#accessories\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle headingLeft productCat\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: capitalize;\\">Accessories</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\\">Looking to improve your space? Our high-quality <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-accessories/\\">accessories</a> include headrests, towel warmers, and footrests. These will help you do just that. Small changes can have a surprisingly large impact on the overall treatment experience.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-accessories/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row\\" equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" parallax=\\"content-moving\\" parallax_image=\\"1484\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"specialSec\\"][vc_column el_class=\\"headingLeft center\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-content\\"]\\n<h3 style=\\"text-align: center; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 4px;\\">OUR SPECIALITY</h3>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-content\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: center; font-size: 44px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: #555; text-transform: capitalize;\\">Customised to your aesthetics</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-content\\"]\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">Our manufacturing unit empowers you to personalize your furniture down to the last detail. Choose from a spectrum of wood stain colours and upholstery options to create a piece that seamlessly integrates with your space. We can even customise the sizes as per your space requirements.This level of customization is ideal for spas and wellness centres seeking to align their interiors, treatment offerings, and client preferences. As experienced spa furniture manufacturers, we ensure that each product not only fits your space but also enhances its purpose and ambience.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"centerBox\\" width=\\"1/6\\" offset=\\"vc_col-sm-offset-2 vc_col-xs-4\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"1893\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"centerBox\\" width=\\"1/6\\" offset=\\"vc_col-sm-offset-1 vc_col-xs-4\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"1895\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"centerBox\\" width=\\"1/6\\" offset=\\"vc_col-sm-offset-1 vc_col-xs-4\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"1894\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row_content\\" equal_height=\\"yes\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"headingSec howWhat\\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft center\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h3 style=\\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 4px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 15px; color: white; font-size: 20px;\\">HOW WE DO</h3>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: center; font-size: 44px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: white; text-transform: capitalize;\\">What We Do</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"color: white; font-size: 18px; text-align: center;\\">Esthetica specializes in precision manufacturing luxury spa furniture, including high-end spa tables, massage bed ranges, spa treatment tables, and Ayurveda tables. We offer a comprehensive range of products tailored for hotel and resort spas. Our cutting-edge manufacturing facility boasts a modern setup. Esthetica handles every aspect of the manufacturing process with meticulous care and expertise. Your vision is our priority, and our capabilities span the entire spectrum of furniture production.</p>\\n<p style=\\"color: white; font-size: 18px; text-align: center;\\">Our in-house team works closely with architects, designers, and spa consultants to deliver solutions that meet global standards. As trusted massage table manufacturers and spa table manufacturers, we combine craftsmanship with innovation to provide spa furniture that performs beautifully, day after day.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"project-sec\\"][vc_column_inner][wolfe_client_logos autoplay_timeout=\\"5000\\" img_ids=\\"5355,5356,5357,5358,5359,5360,5361,5362,5363,5364,5365,5366,5367,5368,5369,5370,5371,5372,5373,5374,5375,5376,5377,5378,5379,5380,5381,5382,5383,5384,5385,5386,5387,5388,5389,5390,5391,5392,5393\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row\\" equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"clientsSec\\"][vc_column css=\\".vc_custom_1465560529987{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\\" el_class=\\"headingLeft center\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h3 style=\\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 4px; font-size: 20px;\\">OUR CLIENTS</h3>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: center; font-size: 44px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: #555; text-transform: capitalize;\\">Across The Globe</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 18px; text-align: center;\\">We are loved around the globe. Our products are used by World-Class spa and Hospitality brands like Marriott, WTS International, Hyatt, ITC, Six Senses, Four Seasons, Sun Siyam, Trident, Holiday Inn, Lux Resorts and many luxury spa projects across the globe.Our reputation as trusted spa furniture manufacturers is built on consistent quality, elegant design, and reliable global service. Leading wellness brands choose us not just for our products, but for the long-term value we bring to their spa environments.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_client_logos autoplay_timeout=\\"1000\\" animation_delay=\\"0.1\\" img_ids=\\"4603,4599,4598,4597,4596,4595,4594,4593,4591,4590,4589,4587,4586,4585,4584,4583,4582,4581,4580,4578,4577,4576,4574,4573,4571,4570,4569,4568,4567,4565,4564,4563,4562,4561,4560,4557,4555,4554,4553,4552,4551,4550,4546,4541,4548,4547,4545\\"][vc_empty_space height=\\"50px\\"][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See All\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/index.php/clients/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\\".vc_custom_1750397385122{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\\"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: center; font-size: 44px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: #555; text-transform: capitalize;\\">Testimonials</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_raw_html css=\\"\\"]JTBBJTVCdHJ1c3RpbmRleCUyMG5vLXJlZ2lzdHJhdGlvbiUzRGdvb2dsZSU1RA==[/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: center; font-size: 44px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: #555; text-transform: capitalize;\\">FAQ</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_toggle title=\\"Can Esthetica furniture be customized to match our spa's design concept?\\" size=\\"lg\\" custom_font_container=\\"tag:h2|font_size:25px|text_align:left|color:%23555555\\" custom_google_fonts=\\"font_family:Josefin%20Sans%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\\" css=\\"\\" use_custom_heading=\\"true\\"]Yes. All Esthetica products are available in a wide range of upholstery colours, base finishes, wood veneers, and fabric options. Custom dimensions and bespoke configurations are available on request.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\\"Are your products suitable for five-star hotel and resort spas?\\" size=\\"lg\\" custom_font_container=\\"tag:h2|font_size:25px|text_align:left|color:%23555555\\" custom_google_fonts=\\"font_family:Josefin%20Sans%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\\" css=\\"\\" use_custom_heading=\\"true\\"]Esthetica furniture is supplied to leading luxury hospitality brands including Six Senses, Raffles, Four Seasons, and Shangri-La. All products are designed to meet the operational and aesthetic demands of high-volume professional environments.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\\"Where is Esthetica furniture manufactured?\\" size=\\"lg\\" custom_font_container=\\"tag:h2|font_size:25px|text_align:left|color:%23555555\\" custom_google_fonts=\\"font_family:Josefin%20Sans%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\\" css=\\"\\" use_custom_heading=\\"true\\"]All products are manufactured at our 34,000 sq. ft. facility in IMT Manesar, Gurgaon, India, using machinery sourced from Italy, Germany, and Taiwan.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\\"How can I become an authorized Esthetica distributor?\\" size=\\"lg\\" custom_font_container=\\"tag:h2|font_size:25px|text_align:left|color:%23555555\\" custom_google_fonts=\\"font_family:Josefin%20Sans%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\\" css=\\"\\" use_custom_heading=\\"true\\"]We welcome enquiries from established distributors in markets where we are currently expanding. Please contact us with details of your company and territory.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\\"Can I visit the Esthetica facility before placing an order?\\" size=\\"lg\\" custom_font_container=\\"tag:h2|font_size:25px|text_align:left|color:%23555555\\" custom_google_fonts=\\"font_family:Josefin%20Sans%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\\" css=\\"\\" use_custom_heading=\\"true\\"]Yes. We welcome visits to our manufacturing facility and showroom in IMT Manesar, Gurgaon. Please contact us to schedule an appointment.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\\"What warranty do Esthetica products carry?\\" size=\\"lg\\" custom_font_container=\\"tag:h2|font_size:25px|text_align:left|color:%23555555\\" custom_google_fonts=\\"font_family:Josefin%20Sans%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\\" css=\\"\\" use_custom_heading=\\"true\\"]Every Esthetica product is backed by a comprehensive manufacturer's warranty: 1 year on upholstery and heating elements, 3 years on motors and electronic controls, and 5 years on the internal frame structure. All warranty claims are handled directly by our team at our manufacturing facility in IMT Manesar, Gurgaon.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\\"What sets Esthetica's craftsmanship apart?\\" size=\\"lg\\" custom_font_container=\\"tag:h2|font_size:25px|text_align:left|color:%23555555\\" custom_google_fonts=\\"font_family:Josefin%20Sans%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\\" css=\\"\\" use_custom_heading=\\"true\\"]Every Esthetica product is built using real wood and real wood veneer — never laminates or synthetic substitutes. Structural components are precision CNC-machined, and all upholstery is hand-finished in-house by our skilled craftsmen. The result is furniture that combines manufacturing precision with genuine handcraft, built to perform in the world's most demanding luxury spa environments.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\\"Do you ship internationally?\\" size=\\"lg\\" custom_font_container=\\"tag:h2|font_size:25px|text_align:left|color:%23555555\\" custom_google_fonts=\\"font_family:Josefin%20Sans%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\\" css=\\"\\" use_custom_heading=\\"true\\"]Yes. Esthetica ships worldwide with an established distributor network across the UK, UAE, Australia, Germany, Belgium, and the USA.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\\"What is the typical lead time for an order?\\" size=\\"lg\\" custom_font_container=\\"tag:h2|font_size:25px|text_align:left|color:%23555555\\" custom_google_fonts=\\"font_family:Josefin%20Sans%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\\" css=\\"\\" use_custom_heading=\\"true\\"]Lead times vary by product and order volume. Standard lead time is 4–5 weeks. Custom orders may require additional time. Contact us for a confirmed timeline at the time of enquiry.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\\"What is Esthetica’s approach to sustainability?\\" size=\\"lg\\" custom_font_container=\\"tag:h2|font_size:25px|text_align:left|color:%23555555\\" custom_google_fonts=\\"font_family:Josefin%20Sans%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\\" css=\\"\\" use_custom_heading=\\"true\\"]Our commitment to sustainability is built into every stage of production. We use real wood and real wood veneer exclusively — no PVC laminates or plastic substitutes. All wood coatings are low-VOC, reducing harmful emissions during manufacturing and throughout the product’s life. Our upholstery materials are plasticiser and phthalate-free, ensuring they are safe for clients, therapists, and the environment. Packaging is plastic-free — all products are shipped in cardboard and wood packaging only.[/vc_toggle][vc_empty_space height=\\"50px\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]"	PUBLISHED	2015-12-27 08:04:57	Spa Furniture | Spa Treatment Tables | Spa Massage Beds	Esthetica manufactures premium spa furniture high-end Massage Tables, Massage Beds, Pedicure Chairs, Spa Tables, Spa Beds for wellness center. Enquiry Now.	{"Spa Furniture","spa furniture","spa furnitures"}	\N	Spa Furniture | Spa Treatment Tables | Electric Massage Beds	Esthetica manufacturers luxury spa furniture equipment: Massage Tables, Massage Beds, Trolleys, Spa Treatment Table & Bed for SPAS & Wellness	\N	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 07:16:00.491	2026-06-12 05:19:32.966
