.com/\\">Make-Up Chairs</a>:</strong> Enhance your make-up application services with our specialized chairs that offer support and style, creating an inviting space for your clients.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<h3></h3>\\n<h2>Innovative Hair Wash and Shampoo Stations</h2>\\n<p>One of our standout offerings is our high-end hair wash stations and shampoo stations, which are designed to provide an indulgent experience for your clients. These stations come equipped with:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>In-built Massage Functions:</strong> Add a touch of luxury with massage features that promote relaxation and elevate the shampoo experience.</li>\\n<li><strong>Electric Leg Raise Function:</strong> Enhance comfort for your clients with adjustable leg support, making every visit a pampering session.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<h3></h3>\\n<h3>Customization for a Cohesive Look</h3>\\n<p>At Esthetica, we understand the importance of aesthetics in creating a harmonious atmosphere. That’s why we offer customization options for upholstery to match the décor of your spa furniture, ensuring a seamless and unified look throughout your space.</p>\\n<h3>Branding Opportunities</h3>\\n<p>To further enhance your branding, we provide the option to emboss your logo on the upholstery of your salon furniture. This not only adds a personal touch but also reinforces your brand identity, creating a lasting impression on your clients.</p>\\n<h3>Comprehensive Salon Equipment</h3>\\n<p>In addition to our luxurious salon furniture, Esthetica is proud to offer a wide range of salon equipment to complete your setup:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Barber Trolleys:</strong> Keep your workspace organized with our functional and stylish barber trolleys, designed for easy access to tools.</li>\\n<li><strong>Facial Trolleys:</strong> Our facial trolleys are perfect for aestheticians, equipped to hold all your essential products and tools for a streamlined workflow.</li>\\n<li><strong>Hair Trolleys:</strong> Ensure efficiency during hair services with our versatile hair trolleys, designed to keep your tools within reach.</li>\\n<li><strong>Hair Dryers &amp; Irons:</strong> Our high-quality hair dryers and styling irons ensure that your clients leave looking their best.</li>\\n<li><strong>Facial Steamers:</strong> Enhance your facial treatments with our professional-grade facial steamers, designed for effective and relaxing sessions.</li>\\n<li><strong>UV Instrument Sterilizers:</strong> Maintain the highest hygiene standards in your salon with our UV sterilizers, essential for client safety.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<h3></h3>\\n<h3>Elevate Your Salon Experience</h3>\\n<p>At Esthetica, we are dedicated to providing you with the best in salon furniture and equipment. Our commitment to quality, customization, and customer satisfaction sets us apart as your go-to source for all your salon needs. Explore our range today and transform your salon into a haven of comfort and style, ensuring your clients always leave feeling rejuvenated and pampered.</p>\\n<h3>Esthetica’s Global Presence</h3>\\n<p>Esthetica Spa &amp; Salon Resources Pvt Ltd has established a formidable global presence as a leading manufacturer and exporter of premium quality salon chairs and hair wash units. Our products are highly sought after, with <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/international-distributors/\\">international distribution</a> spanning countries such as the <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/\\">UAE</a>, <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/qatar/\\">Qatar</a>, <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/saudi-arabia/\\">Saudi Arabia</a>, Oman, Bahrain, Belgium, the United Kingdom, Australia, South Africa, Poland, and the USA, among others in Asia and Europe. Committed to excellence, we ensure our high-quality offerings reach clients worldwide, facilitated by preferential trade agreements that allow for duty-free exports to Australia, the <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/\\">UAE</a>, and ASEAN countries. This strategic approach not only enhances our competitiveness but also solidifies our reputation as a trusted partner in the wellness industry on a global scale.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_js][/vc_raw_js][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>"	PUBLISHED	2024-10-28 14:28:44	Explore Premium Salon Furniture & Chairs Online At Esthetica	Buy salon & barber chairs, hair styling chairs, and makeup chairs crafted for elegance and comfort. Perfect for salons, studios, and beauty professionals.	{"Salon Furniture","Barber Chair","Salon Chair","Salon Furniture Supplier","shampoo chair"}	\N	Salon Furniture: Barber, Styling, Shampoo, & Salon Chairs	Find the perfect salon furniture for hotels, home spas, or resorts. Quality designs that blend beauty and functionality.	\N	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 07:16:00.579	2026-06-12 05:19:33.034
