cmq0lbiz805a6cgcbuiokq811	Spa Relaxation Loungers	spa-relaxation-loungers	DEFAULT	"<p>[vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row_content\\" el_class=\\"product-pages\\"][vc_column][vc_raw_html css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-filter\\"][/vc_raw_html][ess_grid alias=\\"grid-4\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"section-div-p\\"]</p>\\n<div class=\\"div-title\\" style=\\"text-align: center; color: #3e3b3b;\\">\\n<p>Welcome to Esthetica:</p>\\n<h1>Your Destination for Premium Relaxation Beds</h1>\\n</div>\\n<p>At Esthetica, we believe that relaxation should be a luxurious experience, whether indoors or outdoors. Our exquisite range of relaxation beds is designed to elevate any space, combining functionality, comfort, and style. Crafted from the finest materials and designed with meticulous attention to detail, our beds are perfect for both residential and commercial settings, including hotels and resorts.</p>\\n<h3>Outdoor Poolside Loungers</h3>\\n<p>Transform your outdoor space with our premium quality relaxation beds, specifically designed for poolside areas. Our loungers are expertly crafted from solid teak wood using traditional tenon and mortise joinery, ensuring exceptional durability and stability. Each piece is finished with marine-grade wood adhesives and treated with Italian outdoor wood coatings, making them resilient against the harshest weather conditions.</p>\\n<h3>Superior Outdoor Upholstery</h3>\\n<p>Our commitment to quality extends beyond the wood. We utilize premium outdoor upholstery featuring a Nano high-tech compound that enhances longevity and ease of maintenance. This fabric is:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>UV Resistant:</strong> Protects against sun damage and fading.</li>\\n<li><strong>Oil Resistant:</strong> Easy to clean and maintain.</li>\\n<li><strong>Weather Resistant:</strong> Stands up to rain and humidity.</li>\\n<li><strong>Disinfectant Resistant:</strong> Suitable for high-traffic areas and ensures hygiene.</li>\\n<li><strong>Salt Water and Chlorine Resistant:</strong> Perfect for poolside environments.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p>With these features, our loungers are not only comfortable but also practical for any outdoor setting.</p>\\n<h3>Indoor Spa Loungers</h3>\\n<p>In addition to our outdoor offerings, Esthetica provides a stunning collection of indoor spa loungers, available in both electric and non-electric models. Our indoor loungers are designed to provide optimal comfort, making them ideal for spa settings, wellness centres, or relaxation areas in hotels.</p>\\n<h2>Electric Spa Relaxation Loungers</h2>\\n<p>Our powered spa loungers take relaxation to the next level with advanced features designed for ultimate convenience:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Electronic Backrest and Leg Rest Adjustments:</strong> Customize your position for maximum comfort.</li>\\n<li><strong>Detachable Reading Lamp:</strong> Enjoy your favourite book or magazine while you relax.</li>\\n<li><strong>USB Charging Socket:</strong> Stay connected even while you unwind.</li>\\n<li><strong>In-built Heating Function:</strong> Add an extra layer of comfort with adjustable warmth.</li>\\n<li><strong>Foldable Lateral Shelf Support:</strong> Convenient for personal items or refreshments.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p>These electric loungers are perfect for creating a luxurious spa experience, ensuring your clients can fully unwind and indulge in relaxation.</p>\\n<h3>Non-Electric Spa Relaxation Beds</h3>\\n<p>For those who prefer a more traditional approach, our non-electric relaxation beds are ergonomically designed for maximum comfort. These versatile beds can be used indoors or in wet areas, offering a seamless blend of functionality and style. The ergonomic design, combined with comfortable upholstery and foam cushioning, ensures that every client enjoys a restorative experience.</p>\\n<h3>Customization for Your Unique Space</h3>\\n<p>At Esthetica, we understand that every space is unique. As a factory producing these spa loungers, we offer customization options to meet your specific needs. You can personalize the following aspects:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Size:</strong> Tailor the dimensions to fit your space perfectly.</li>\\n<li><strong>Wood Finish:</strong> Choose from a variety of finishes to match your decor.</li>\\n<li><strong>Upholstery Colour:</strong> Select the ideal colour to complement your design scheme.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p>With our custom options, you can create relaxation beds that are not only functional but also enhance the aesthetic of your spa or resort.</p>\\n<h3>Why Choose Esthetica?</h3>\\n<p>When you choose Esthetica, you are choosing quality, craftsmanship, and innovation. Our dedication to using the finest materials and advanced technology sets us apart from the competition. We strive to ensure that every relaxation bed we produce meets the highest standards, allowing you to offer an unparalleled experience to your clients.</p>\\n<h3>Exceptional Customer Support</h3>\\n<p>Our commitment to customer satisfaction doesn’t end with your purchase. We provide exceptional customer support to assist you in selecting the right products and addressing any questions or concerns you may have. Our knowledgeable team is always here to help you create the perfect relaxation environment.</p>\\n<h3>Elevate Your Space Today</h3>\\n<p>Enhance your indoor and outdoor relaxation areas with Esthetica's premium relaxation beds. Explore our collection and discover the perfect loungers to complement your <a href=\\"https://www.portablemassagebed.in/\\">spa</a> or resort. Contact us today to learn more about our products and customization options, and let us help you create a haven of relaxation for your clients. Choose Esthetica for an unmatched blend of luxury and functionality!</p>\\n<h3>Esthetica’s Global Presence</h3>\\n<p>Esthetica Spa &amp; Salon Resources Pvt Ltd has installed its spa relaxation loungers in many premium spa resorts and hotels, spas across the globe. The Bodhi Spa in the USA and Wai Araki in New Zealand are using <strong>Mandakani Spa Relaxation Loungers</strong>.  Our products are highly sought after, with <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/international-distributors/\\">international distribution</a> spanning countries such as the <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/\\">UAE</a>, <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/qatar/\\">Qatar</a>, <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/saudi-arabia/\\">Saudi Arabia</a>, Oman, Bahrain, Belgium, the United Kingdom, Australia, South Africa, Poland, and the USA, among others in Asia and Europe. Committed to excellence, we ensure our high-quality offerings reach clients worldwide, facilitated by preferential trade agreements that allow for duty-free exports to Australia, the <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/\\">UAE</a>, and ASEAN countries. This strategic approach not only enhances our competitiveness but also solidifies our reputation as a trusted partner in the wellness industry on a global scale.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_js][/vc_raw_js][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>"	PUBLISHED	2024-10-28 15:23:04	Buy Spa Relaxation Beds with Cushioned Loungers – Esthetica	Buy spa relaxation beds designed for ultimate comfort. Explore cushioned loungers ideal for spas, wellness centers, and luxury retreats. Shop Esthetica now.	{"Spa Relaxation Lounger",Loungers,"Relaxation Loungers","Poolside Lounge",Lounger}	\N	Spa Relaxation Bed - Wave Poolside Loungers - Outdoor Lounge	Discover the Spa Relaxation Lounger for ultimate comfort and luxury in your indoor or outdoor space.	\N	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 07:16:00.597	2026-06-12 05:19:33.044
cmq0lbizg05a7cgcbikcjr5i0	Spa Accessories	spa-accessories	DEFAULT	"[vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row_content\\" el_class=\\"product-pages\\"][vc_column][vc_raw_html css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-filter\\"][/vc_raw_html][ess_grid alias=\\"grid-5\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"section-div-p\\"]\\n<div class=\\"div-title\\" style=\\"text-align: center; color: #3e3b3b;\\">\\n\\nWelcome to Esthetica:\\n<h1>Your Premier Source for Spa Equipment and Accessories</h1>\\n</div>\\nAt Esthetica, we understand that sourcing the right equipment and accessories for your spa or salon can often feel like a daunting task. Coordinating with multiple suppliers for essential yet often overlooked items can drain your time and energy. That’s why we’re here—to simplify your job and help you focus on what you do best: providing exceptional services to your clients.\\n<h3>Curated Collections for Every Need</h3>\\nWe pride ourselves on offering a carefully curated collection of spa equipment and accessories, designed specifically for professionals in the beauty and wellness industry. Our extensive range of products ensures that you have everything you need to create an inviting and effective environment for your clients. From the essentials to the unique touches that enhance the spa experience, Esthetica has you covered.\\n<h3>Our Offerings Include:</h3>\\n<ul>\\n \\t<li><strong>Massage Table Warmers:</strong> Enhance client comfort with our reliable and efficient <a href=\\"https://www.portablemassagebed.in/\\">massage table</a> warmers. Perfect for those chilly days, they ensure a soothing and relaxing experience.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Massage Oil Warmers:</strong> Set the mood for relaxation with our massage oil warmers, designed to heat oils to the perfect temperature for treatments.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Massage Stone Heaters &amp; Stones:</strong> Deliver the ultimate in relaxation with our quality <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/massage-stones/\\">massage stones</a> and heaters, allowing for a rejuvenating hot stone massage.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Copper Pedicure Bowls:</strong> Bring a touch of elegance to your spa with our beautiful copper pedicure bowls, ideal for enhancing your pedicure services.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Foot Soak Bowls &amp; Manicure Bowls:</strong> Our selection of foot soak and manicure bowls are designed for comfort and durability, making them a staple in any salon.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Service Trays &amp; Oil Tester Trays:</strong> Keep your workspace organized and efficient with our stylish service trays, ensuring a seamless experience for both you and your clients.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Do Not Disturb Door Signs:</strong> Maintain a serene atmosphere in your massage room with our discreet and professional door signs.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Singing Bowls &amp; Tingsha Bells:</strong> Incorporate sound therapy into your practice with our beautifully crafted singing bowls and tingsha bells, enhancing the relaxation experience.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Aroma Oil Burners:</strong> Create a soothing ambiance with our aroma oil burners, perfect for diffusing calming scents throughout your spa.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Hot Towel Cabinets &amp; Towel Warmers:</strong> Provide a luxurious touch to your services with our hot towel cabinets and warmers, ensuring your towels are always at the perfect temperature.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>UV Sterilizers:</strong> Maintain the highest standards of hygiene with our UV sterilizers, essential for ensuring your tools and accessories are safe for every client.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<h3>Simplifying Your Experience</h3>\\nAt Esthetica, we believe that sourcing high-quality spa equipment should be straightforward and stress-free. By centralizing your shopping experience, we save you valuable time, allowing you to focus on providing exceptional care to your clients. Our commitment to quality means you can trust that every product you purchase meets the highest industry standards.\\n<h3>Why Choose Esthetica?</h3>\\n<ul>\\n \\t<li><strong>Curated Quality:</strong> Each product is handpicked to ensure it meets the needs of modern spas and salons.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Expert Support:</strong> Our knowledgeable team is always ready to assist you in finding the perfect products for your specific needs.</li>\\n \\t<li><strong>Convenience:</strong> Enjoy the ease of sourcing all your spa essentials from one trusted provider.</li>\\n</ul>\\nElevate your spa or salon experience today with Esthetica. Explore our curated collection and discover how we can simplify your sourcing process, allowing you to create a truly relaxing environment for your clients. Your journey to a better spa experience starts here!\\n<h2>Esthetica’s Global Presence</h2>\\nEsthetica Spa &amp; Salon Resources Pvt Ltd has established a formidable global presence as a leading manufacturer and exporter of premium quality brass and copper pedicure bowls and accessories. Our products are highly sought after, with <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/international-distributors/\\">international distribution</a> spanning countries such as the <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/\\">UAE</a>, <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/qatar/\\">Qatar</a>, <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/saudi-arabia/\\">Saudi Arabia</a>, Oman, Bahrain, Belgium, the United Kingdom, Australia, South Africa, Poland, and the USA, among others in Asia and Europe. Committed to excellence, we ensure our high-quality offerings reach clients worldwide, facilitated by preferential trade agreements that allow for duty-free exports to Australia, the <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/\\">UAE</a>, and ASEAN countries. This strategic approach not only enhances our competitiveness but also solidifies our reputation as a trusted partner in the wellness industry on a global scale.\\n\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_js][/vc_raw_js][/vc_column][/vc_row]"	PUBLISHED	2024-10-28 15:46:12	Buy Spa Accessories with Premium Equipment Online – Esthetica	Buy spa accessories and premium equipment online from Esthetica. Explore high-quality tools and essentials for professional spa and salon setups. Visit now!	{"Spa Accessories & Equipment"}	\N	Spa Accessories & Equipment: The Key to a Successful Salon	Discover a carefully curated collection of spa equipment and accessories for professionals in the beauty salon and wellness industry.	\N	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 07:16:00.604	2026-06-12 05:19:33.05
