inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row\\" equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" parallax=\\"content-moving\\" parallax_image=\\"1484\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"specialSec\\"][vc_column el_class=\\"headingLeft center\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-content\\"]\\n<h3 style=\\"text-align: center; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 4px;\\">OUR SPECIALITY</h3>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-content\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: center; font-size: 44px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: #555; text-transform: capitalize;\\">Customised to your aesthetics</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-content\\"]\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">Our manufacturing unit empowers you to personalize your furniture down to the last detail. Choose from a spectrum of wood stain colours and upholstery options to create a piece that seamlessly integrates with your space. We can even customise the sizes as per your space requirements.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"centerBox\\" width=\\"1/6\\" offset=\\"vc_col-sm-offset-2 vc_col-xs-4\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"1893\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"centerBox\\" width=\\"1/6\\" offset=\\"vc_col-sm-offset-1 vc_col-xs-4\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"1895\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"centerBox\\" width=\\"1/6\\" offset=\\"vc_col-sm-offset-1 vc_col-xs-4\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"1894\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row_content\\" equal_height=\\"yes\\" ov