cmq0lbj0g05abcgcb5tdga2bq	Spa Stools	spa-stools	DEFAULT	"[vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row_content\\" el_class=\\"product-pages\\"][vc_column][vc_raw_html css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-filter\\"][/vc_raw_html][ess_grid alias=\\"grid-7\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"section-div-p\\"]\\n<div class=\\"div-title\\" style=\\"text-align: center; color: #3e3b3b;\\">\\n<h1>Discover Our Exquisite Range of Spa Stools</h1>\\n</div>\\nAt Esthetica, we offer a carefully curated selection of spa stools that blend functionality and style to enhance your treatment spaces. Our product range includes a variety of handcrafted solid wood spa stools, perfect for indoor use in treatment rooms. These durable and elegant stools add a touch of sophistication to any spa environment.\\n\\nFor therapists on the go, our easy-to-carry folding therapist stools provide a practical solution without compromising comfort. Additionally, our low-height pedicurist chairs and stools are specifically designed for manicure and pedicure areas, ensuring that your clients enjoy a comfortable experience while you work.\\n\\nOur designer spa therapist chairs feature stylish wooden backrests, combining aesthetics with ergonomic support. For medical and beauty treatment rooms, we offer stools crafted with aluminum alloy bases and stainless steel components, ensuring durability and ease of maintenance.\\n\\nMost of our wooden stools are fixed-height, providing stability, while our other designs come equipped with gas lifts for height adjustment and castor wheels for effortless mobility around the treatment room. This versatility allows you to tailor your workspace to meet the needs of each client and service.\\n\\nCustomization is key at <a href=\\"https://www.estheticamedicalfurniture.com/\\">Esthetica</a>. The upholstery of our attendant chairs can be personalized to match your massage or treatment table upholstery, creating a cohesive and visually appealing environment that enhances the overall experience for your clients.\\n\\nTransform your spa or treatment room with our premium spa stools, designed for comfort, functionality, and style. Explore our collection today and discover the perfect seating solutions to elevate your service offerings!\\n<h2>Esthetica’s Global Presence</h2>\\nEsthetica Spa &amp; Salon Resources Pvt Ltd has established a formidable global presence as a leading manufacturer and exporter of premium quality spa stools and therapist chairs. Our <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-carts/\\">spa carts</a> are highly sought after, with <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/international-distributors/\\">international distribution</a> spanning countries such as the <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/\\">UAE</a>, <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/qatar/\\">Qatar</a>, <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/saudi-arabia/\\">Saudi Arabia</a>, Oman, Maldives, Hong Kong, Bahrain, Belgium, the United Kingdom, Australia, South Africa, Poland, and the USA, among others in Asia and Europe. Committed to excellence, we ensure our high-quality offerings reach clients worldwide, facilitated by preferential trade agreements that allow for duty-free exports to Australia, the <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/uae/\\">UAE</a>, and ASEAN countries. This strategic approach not only enhances our competitiveness but also solidifies our reputation as a trusted partner in the wellness industry on a global scale.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_js][/vc_raw_js][/vc_column][/vc_row]"	PUBLISHED	2024-10-28 15:57:39	Spa Stools & Therapist Chairs | Premium Pedicurist Stools	Buy durable spa stools for salons and wellness spaces. Stylish pedicurist stool options available. Therapist chair with adjustable height and comfort. Visit Now!	{"Spa Stools"}	\N	Spa Stools & Therapist Chairs | Premium Pedicurist Stools	Buy durable spa stools for salons and wellness spaces. Stylish pedicurist stool options available. Therapist chair with adjustable height and comfort. Visit Now!	\N	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 07:16:00.641	2026-06-12 05:19:33.089
cmq6clt54001rcgkez49gxcw7	About	about-us	DEFAULT	"<p>[vc_row overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"aboutHead\\"][vc_column el_class=\\"headingLeft\\"][wolfe_title_desc_header title=\\"About us\\" sub_title=\\"Who we are\\" font_size_sub_title=\\"\\" short_desc=\\"Welcome to Esthetica – Your pinnacle of elegance and functionality in Spa, Wellness, and Healthcare Furniture. Established in 2011, Esthetica takes pride in being a distinguished manufacturer of premium spa and wellness furniture. Over the years, we have evolved into a leading brand, expanding our expertise to include the production of top-quality Medical Furniture.\\" font_size_desc=\\"\\" title_color=\\"\\" sub_title_color=\\"\\" short_desc_color=\\"\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row\\" parallax=\\"content-moving\\" parallax_image=\\"1773\\" overlay_row=\\"rgba(0,0,0,0.6)\\" el_class=\\"bgCover teamCall\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1465548756884{padding-top: 15% !important;padding-bottom: 15% !important;}\\"][vc_column][no_simple_title title=\\"We are a team of professionals and skilled craftsmen committed to producing high-quality Treatment tables for spas, wellness centres and medical clinics.\\" title_font_size=\\"\\" title_color=\\"#ffffff\\" undeline=\\"no_underliner\\" title_align=\\"align_center\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_row=\\"\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1465561764556{margin-top: 10% !important;}\\"][vc_column width=\\"2/3\\" offset=\\"vc_col-sm-offset-2\\" el_class=\\"subHead\\"][no_simple_title title=\\"We deliver a diverse product range on time, every time with quick lead times using modern woodworking machines\\" title_font_size=\\"\\" undeline=\\"no_underliner\\" title_align=\\"align_center\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1465561607675{margin-bottom: 10% !important;}\\"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"font-size18\\"]Our commitment to excellence has made us a trusted choice for distributors, spa management companies, and spa consultants worldwide, with our products being loved, used, and recommended on a global scale.</p>\\n<p>At the heart of our success is a state-of-the-art manufacturing facility spanning 34,000 square feet, equipped with cutting-edge technology and operated by a skilled team of more than 100 dedicated professionals.</p>\\n<p>Our mission at Esthetica is clear – to manufacture top-of-the-line furniture for the spa, wellness, and healthcare sectors.  We prioritize using the finest raw materials and adhering to the best manufacturing practices, ensuring that each product not only meets but exceeds industry standards.</p>\\n<p>What sets us apart is our relentless pursuit of perfection. We go beyond merely crafting furniture; we curate experiences. Every design is a thoughtful blend of aesthetics and practicality, resulting in furniture that elevates the ambiance of spas, wellness centers, and healthcare facilities alike.</p>\\n<p>Esthetica remains dedicated to pushing the boundaries of what is possible in <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/massage-tables/\\">spa</a> and <a href=\\"https://www.estheticamedicalfurniture.com/\\">healthcare furniture</a>. We invite you to explore our range of meticulously crafted products and join us in the pursuit of creating spaces that redefine comfort, style, and sophistication.</p>\\n<p>Esthetica – Where Form Meets Function, and Luxury is a Standard.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text][wonderplugin_carousel id=\\"1\\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row\\" parallax=\\"content-moving\\" parallax_image=\\"1439\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"aboutCall\\"][vc_column][no_simple_title title=\\"We are always ready to work for exciting and ambitious clients. If you love our products, please get in touch.\\" title_font_size=\\"\\" undeline=\\"no_underliner\\" title_align=\\"align_center\\"][vc_empty_space height=\\"50px\\"][vc_btn title=\\"Let's Collaborate\\" shape=\\"square\\" color=\\"inverse\\" size=\\"lg\\" align=\\"center\\" css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\"\\" link=\\"url:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spafurniture.in%2Fcontact-us%2F|title:Let's%20Collaborate\\" el_class=\\"Let's Collaborate\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>"	PUBLISHED	2015-12-09 07:49:10	About Esthetica | Premium Spa Furniture Manufacturer	Esthetica supplies spa furniture to top wellness brands worldwide, expertly crafted for superior comfort, long-lasting durability, and luxury design. Visit Now!	{"spa furniture manufacturer","spa furniture manufacturers in india","spa furniture manufacturers"}	\N	About Esthetica | Premium Spa Furniture Manufacturer	Esthetica supplies spa furniture to top wellness brands worldwide, expertly crafted for superior comfort, long-lasting durability, and luxury design. Visit Now!	cmq0kzrnj01c5cgcbmv3vynbf	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-09 07:58:40.84	2026-06-26 01:38:55.029
cmq0lbj0o05accgcb06hja4ls	Saudi Arabia	saudi-arabia	DEFAULT	"[vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row_content\\" full_height=\\"yes\\" equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"proRotate home-page-graphic-for-nov\\"][vc_column el_class=\\"vertMid\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"none\\"]\\n<div id=\\"gifSection\\" class=\\"image-360\\"><img class=\\"aligncenter wp-image-4405 size-full\\" src=\\"/uploads/1781241018015-kb54m1mrz6n.gif\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"1024\\" height=\\"772\\" /></div>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" el_class=\\"proText\\"]\\n<h6>Featured Here <strong>The Shirodhara Massage Bed</strong></h6>\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row\\" parallax=\\"content-moving\\" parallax_image=\\"1439\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"callAction1\\"][vc_column el_class=\\"callBtn\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_id=\\"div-1\\"]\\n<h1 style=\\"font-size: 28px;\\"><strong>الشركة الرائدة في تصنيع أثاث السبا الفاخر في المملكة العربية السعودية</strong></h1>\\nتُعتبر إستيتكا شركة رائدة في تصنيع وتوريد أثاث السبا عالي الجودة في المملكة العربية السعودية. مع التزام قوي بالجودة والتصميم العصري، نقدم مجموعة متنوعة من المنتجات، بما في ذلك طاولات التدليك الفاخرة، وأسرّة التدليك الكهربائية، ومحطات البيديكير، وكراسي الاسترخاء في السبا، ومجموعة رائعة من أثاث صالونات التجميل. تتميز منتجاتنا بتقنيات متطورة، وميزات قابلة للتعديل، وتصاميم مريحة لضمان أقصى درجات الراحة والوظيفية.\\n\\nموزعنا المعتمد، ماضي انترناشيونال، يعمل في الرياض وجدة والخبر. تلتزم ماضي انترناشيونال بتوزيع وتعزيز عروضنا من أثاث السبا والصالونات عبر هذه المدن، مما يضمن أن تكون المنتجعات والصالونات الفاخرة قادرة على الوصول إلى منتجاتنا العالية الجودة.\\n\\n<strong>الرياض، المملكة العربية السعودية</strong>\\n\\nدار ماضي انترناشيونال و.ل.ل. السليمانية، شارع الذهّاب تقاطع شارع الملك عبد العزيز الرياض – المملكة العربية السعودية ص.ب: 25862، الرمز البريدي 11476\\n\\n<strong>جدة، المملكة العربية السعودية</strong>\\n\\nدار ماضي انترناشيونال و.ل.ل. مكتب رقم 501B، الطابق الخامس، المبنى B شارع الأمير محمد بن عبد العزيز - مركز بن عمران جدة – المملكة العربية السعودية ص.ب: 25862، الرمز البريدي 11476\\n\\n<strong>الخبر</strong>\\n\\nدار ماضي انترناشيونال و.ل.ل. الطابق السادس، البرجين التوأميين البندريه، طريق الملك سلمان الخبر – المملكة العربية السعودية ص.ب: 25862، الرمز البريدي 11476\\n\\nللاستفسارات ولمزيد من المعلومات حول منتجاتنا، يُرجى التواصل معنا على <a href=\\"mailto:madi.international@spafurniture.in\\">madi.international@spafurniture.in</a>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_id=\\"div-2\\"]\\n<h1 style=\\"font-size: 28px;\\"><strong>Leading Manufacturer of Premium Spa Furniture in Saudi Arabia</strong></h1>\\nEsthetica is a premier manufacturer and supplier of high-quality spa furniture in Saudi Arabia. With a strong commitment to quality and modern design, we offer a diverse range of products, including premium massage tables, electric massage beds, pedicure stations, spa relaxation loungers, and an exquisite collection of salon furniture. Our products are equipped with sophisticated technologies, adjustable features, and ergonomic designs to ensure optimal comfort and functionality.\\n\\nOur authorized distributor, Madi International, operates in Riyadh, Jeddah, and Al Khobar. Madi International is dedicated to distributing and promoting our spa and salon furniture offerings across these cities, ensuring that luxury spas and salons have access to our premium-quality products.[/vc_column_text][vc_raw_html css=\\"\\" el_id=\\"div-3\\"][/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_id=\\"div-4\\"]For inquiries and further information about our products, please reach out to us at <a href=\\"mailto:madi.international@spafurniture.in\\"><strong>madi.international@spafurniture.in</strong></a>[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\\"English\\" style=\\"outline\\" color=\\"chino\\" size=\\"lg\\" align=\\"center\\" css=\\"\\" el_id=\\"button-id\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"headingSec\\"][vc_column width=\\"1/3\\" el_class=\\"headingLeft\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733484215514{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 class=\\"ts-head-title headingLeft\\">Our Products</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733402205989{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; line-height: 1.2; text-transform: none;\\">Crafted\\ntill Perfection</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\\"2/3\\" el_class=\\"headingDesc\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\"]Explore our new collection, featuring high-end electric massage beds, specialized spa tables for Ayurvedic Treatments, Relaxation Loungers, Spa Trolleys, Foot Reflexology Chairs, and Pedicure Chairs. Each piece is meticulously crafted to enhance the ambience and functionality of your spa &amp; salon.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"productC\\"][vc_column][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg1\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"4731\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#massage-beds\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft productCat vMiddle\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733402228933{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; line-height: 1.2; text-transform: none;\\">Massage Beds</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\\"25px\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Our Massage Table collection features many premium options to suit every professional need. From <strong>Electric Massage Beds, Portable Massage Table,</strong> <strong>Hydraulic Massage Tables</strong>, <strong>Wooden Massage Beds</strong> to <strong>Ayurvedic Treatment Tables</strong> and <strong>Low-Height Thai Massage Beds</strong>, we offer versatility and comfort. Our collection also includes <strong>Portable Massage Tables</strong>, <strong>Electric Treatment Beds</strong> for aesthetic clinics, and <strong>Facial Beds</strong> for salons and spas, ensuring superior quality for every treatment setting.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/massage-beds/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft productCat vMiddle\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733402254117{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; line-height: 1.2; text-transform: none;\\">Spa Stools</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\\"25px\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Discover our premium collection of <strong>spa stools, pedicure stools,</strong> and <strong>therapist chairs</strong> for spa and aesthetic treatment rooms. We offer <strong>low-height pedicurist stools</strong> and <strong>folding therapist stools</strong>, all crafted for ultimate comfort, stability, durability, and style in your treatment space.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-stools/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg3\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"1537\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#spa-stools\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg2\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"1970\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#spa-trolleys\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle headingLeft productCat\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733402278236{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; line-height: 1.2; text-transform: none;\\">Spa Trolleys</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\\"25px\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Our Spa Trolley Collection offers versatile solutions for spas and aesthetic clinics. Choose from <strong>Massage Stone Heater Trolleys</strong>, <strong>Spa Carts</strong>  for Hot Cabi, <strong>Salon Trolleys</strong>, <strong>Barber Shop Trolleys</strong>, and <strong>Wooden Spa Trolleys</strong>, designed for easy mobility and efficient storage of all your spa essentials.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-trolleys/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft productCat vMiddle\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733402305341{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; line-height: 1.2; text-transform: none;\\">Pedicure &amp;\\nManicure</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\\"25px\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Esthetica's Pedicure &amp; Manicure range offers luxurious and functional solutions for nail professionals. Our collection includes <strong>Luxury Pedicure Chairs</strong>, <strong>Manicure Pedicure Chairs</strong>, <strong>Manicure Table, </strong><strong>Professional Manicure Stations</strong>, and <strong>Compact Nail Tables</strong> designed for comfort and style. We also provide <strong>Pedicure Stations</strong> with and without plumbing options and ergonomic <strong>Pedicurist Chairs</strong>, ensuring the perfect setup for any salon or spa.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/manicure-pedicure-chairs/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg5\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"4703\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#pedicure-manicure\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg7\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"2685\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#loungers\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft productCat vMiddle\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733402332052{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; li