cmq0lbj1905aecgcbkvzz6mqn	Qatar	qatar	DEFAULT	"[vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row_content\\" full_height=\\"yes\\" equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"proRotate home-page-graphic-for-nov\\"][vc_column el_class=\\"vertMid\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"none\\"]\\n<div id=\\"gifSection\\" class=\\"image-360\\"><img class=\\"aligncenter wp-image-4405 size-full\\" src=\\"/uploads/1781241018015-kb54m1mrz6n.gif\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"1024\\" height=\\"772\\" /></div>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" el_class=\\"proText\\"]\\n<h6>Featured Here <strong>The Shirodhara Massage Bed</strong></h6>\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row\\" parallax=\\"content-moving\\" parallax_image=\\"1439\\" overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"callAction1\\"][vc_column el_class=\\"callBtn\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_id=\\"div-1\\"]\\n<h1 style=\\"font-size: 28px;\\"><strong>الشركة الرائدة في تصنيع أثاث السبا الفاخر في قطر</strong></h1>\\nتُعتبر إستيتيكا واحدة من الشركات الرائدة في تصنيع وتوريد أثاث السبا عالي الجودة في قطر. مع التزامنا بالجودة والتصميم العصري، نقدم مجموعة متنوعة من المنتجات تشمل طاولات التدليك عالية الجودة، وأسرة التدليك الكهربائية، ومحطات البيديكير، وكراسي الاسترخاء في السبا، ومجموعة رائعة من أثاث صالونات التجميل. تتضمن منتجاتنا تقنيات متطورة، وميزات قابلة للتعديل، وخصائص مريحة لضمان الراحة والوظيفية.\\n\\nنفتخر بموزعنا المعتمد، ماضي انترناشيونال، في الدوحة. تلتزم ماضي انترناشيونال بتوزيع وتعزيز عروضنا من أثاث السبا والصالونات عبر قطر، لضمان وصول المنتجعات والصالونات الفاخرة إلى منتجاتنا عالية الجودة.\\n\\n<strong>معلومات الاتصال: </strong>\\n\\nماضي انترناشيونال و.ل.ل. شارع السعد، الدوحة - قطر، ص.ب: 234412\\n\\nللاستفسارات ولمزيد من المعلومات حول منتجاتنا، يُرجى التواصل معنا على <a href=\\"mailto:madi.international@spafurniture.in\\">madi.international@spafurniture.in</a>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_id=\\"div-2\\"]\\n<h1 style=\\"font-size: 28px;\\"><strong>Leading Manufacturer of Premium Spa Furniture in Qatar</strong></h1>\\nEsthetica is one of the leading manufacturers and suppliers of premium quality <a href=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/\\">spa furniture</a> in Qatar. With a commitment to quality and modern design, we offer a diverse product range that includes high-quality massage tables, electric massage beds, pedicure stations, spa relaxation loungers and an exquisite collection of salon furniture. Our products incorporate sophisticated technologies, adjustable features, and ergonomic features to ensure comfort and functionality.\\n\\nWe take pride in our authorized distributor, Madi International, located in Doha. Madi International is dedicated to distributing and promoting our spa and salon furniture offerings across Qatar, ensuring that luxury spas and salons have access to our premium-quality products.[/vc_column_text][vc_raw_html css=\\"\\" el_id=\\"div-3\\"][/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_id=\\"div-4\\"]For inquiries and further information about our products, please reach out to us at <a href=\\"mailto:madi.international@spafurniture.in\\"><strong>madi.international@spafurniture.in</strong></a>[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\\"English\\" style=\\"outline\\" color=\\"chino\\" size=\\"lg\\" align=\\"center\\" css=\\"\\" el_id=\\"button-id\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"headingSec\\"][vc_column width=\\"1/3\\" el_class=\\"headingLeft\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733485360088{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 class=\\"ts-head-title headingLeft\\">Our Products</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\\".vc_custom_1733401877744{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; line-height: 1.2; text-transform: none;\\">Crafted\\ntill Perfection</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\\"2/3\\" el_class=\\"headingDesc\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" css=\\"\\"]Explore our latest trending collection, featuring high-end electric massage beds, Ayurvedic Treatments, Relaxation Loungers, Spa Trolleys, Foot Reflexology Chairs, Manicure Stations, Pedicure Stools, Salon Furniture, and Pedicure Chairs. Each piece is diligently hand crafted to enhance the ambience and functionality of your spa and salon space.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_row=\\"\\" el_class=\\"productC\\"][vc_column][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg1\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"4731\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#massage-beds\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft productCat vMiddle\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733401869672{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; line-height: 1.2; text-transform: none;\\">Massage Beds</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\\"25px\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Esthetica's Massage Table collection features many premium options to suit every professional need. From <strong>Electric Massage Beds</strong> and <strong>Wooden Massage Beds</strong> to <strong>Ayurvedic Treatment Tables</strong> and <strong>Low-Height Thai Massage Beds</strong>, we offer versatility and comfort. Our collection also includes <strong>Portable Massage Tables</strong>, <strong>Electric Spa Treatment Beds</strong> for aesthetic clinics, and <strong>Facial Beds</strong> for salons and spas, ensuring superior quality for every treatment setting.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"http