umbing options and ergonomic <strong>Pedicurist Chairs</strong>, ensuring the perfect setup for any salon or spa.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/manicure-pedicure-chairs/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg5\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"4703\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#pedicure-manicure\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg7\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"2685\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#loungers\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"headingLeft productCat vMiddle\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733401830297{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; line-height: 1.2; text-transform: none;\\">Loungers</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\\"25px\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Esthetica's Spa Relaxation Lounger range offers the perfect blend of comfort and style for any setting. Choose from luxurious <strong>wave loungers</strong>, <strong>outdoor poolside loungers</strong>, and <strong>indoor relaxation beds</strong>. Our <strong>electric indoor spa loungers</strong> feature an in-built heating function, a detachable reading light, and a convenient lateral shelf, providing ultimate relaxation and convenience for your spa or wellness space.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/spa-relaxation-loungers/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle headingLeft productCat\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\\"fadeInUp\\" css=\\".vc_custom_1733401822001{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\\"]\\n<h2 style=\\"font-size: 44px; color: #4b3718; line-height: 1.2; text-transform: none;\\">Salon Furniture</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\\"25px\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Discover our curated collection of premium salon furniture designed for both style and functionality. We offer <strong>Hair Styling Chairs</strong>, <strong>Bridal Chairs</strong>, <strong>Barber Chairs</strong>, <strong>Hair Color Trolleys</strong>, and <strong>Hair Wash Stations</strong>, each crafted to enhance the comfort and efficiency of your salon. Elevate your space with high-quality, durable modern salon chairs and shampoo stations that provide both luxury and practicality for every client and professional need.</p>\\n[/vc_column_text][wolfe_button text_button=\\"See Collection\\" url_button=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/salon-furniture/\\" choose_border=\\"no_border\\" border_radius=\\"\\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle proImg4\\" width=\\"1/2\\"][vc_single_image image=\\"3935\\" img_size=\\"full\\" alignment=\\"center\\" onclick=\\"custom_link\\" css_animation=\\"bottom-to-top\\" link=\\"https://www.spafurniture.in/products/#salon-furniture\\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator color=\\"custom\\" el_width=\\"80\\" accent_color=\\"#f4ede9\\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\\"yes\\" content_placement=\\"middle\\" overlay_row=\\"\\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\\"vMiddle pro