cmq0lbj1o05agcgcbiw7au4kj	Massage Beds	massage-beds-in-uae	DEFAULT	"[vc_row full_width=\\"stretch_row_content\\" el_class=\\"product-pages\\"][vc_column][vc_raw_html css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"custom-filter\\"][/vc_raw_html][ess_grid alias=\\"grid-2\\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\\"\\" el_class=\\"section-div-p\\"]\\n<h1 style=\\"font-size: 28px; text-align: justify;\\"><b>Welcome to SPA Furniture: Your Premier Destination for Massage Beds in UAE</b></h1>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">At SPA Furniture, we specialize in crafting high-quality </span><b>massage beds in UAE</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> designed to elevate comfort, functionality, and professionalism in spas, wellness centers, salons, and therapy clinics. Our wide range of products caters to every requirement, from versatile electric tables to classic manual beds, ensuring your clients enjoy an exceptional experience while providing therapists with ergonomic, reliable solutions.</span>\\n\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">We understand that every wellness environment is unique, and our solutions are tailored to meet diverse operational needs without compromising on quality or aesthetics.</span>\\n<h2><b>Explore Our Range of Massage Beds in UAE</b></h2>\\n<h3><b>Electric Massage Bed in UAE</b></h3>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Our </span><b>electric massage bed in UAE</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> models are designed for premium convenience and flexibility. With smooth electric adjustments for height, backrest, and leg sections, therapists can customize positions according to client needs. The silent operation ensures uninterrupted relaxation, making these beds ideal for high-end spas, physiotherapy clinics, and wellness centers.</span>\\n<h3><b>Manual and Hydraulic Massage Tables</b></h3>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">For clients seeking cost-effective yet durable options, our </span><b>massage table in UAE</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> range includes manual and hydraulic models. These beds offer strong frames, comfortable padding, and easy height adjustments, making them suitable for traditional spa setups or smaller therapy rooms.</span>\\n<h3><b>Low-Height and Traditional Massage Beds</b></h3>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Designed for Thai massage or other traditional therapies, low-height massage beds provide easy access and mobility for therapists. The ergonomic design supports authentic treatment techniques while keeping clients comfortable throughout the session.</span>\\n<h3><b>Portable Massage Tables</b></h3>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">For mobile therapists or home service providers, our portable massage beds offer stability and durability without sacrificing convenience. Lightweight yet robust, these tables can be transported effortlessly, making them perfect for temporary setups or events.</span>\\n<h3><b>Specialized Massage Beds</b></h3>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">We also provide beds designed for prenatal care, Reiki, and holistic therapies. Each table is crafted to support unique treatments, ensuring client comfort and professional functionality.</span>\\n<h2><b>Customization Options</b></h2>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">At SPA Furniture, being one of the best </span>massage bed manufacturers in UAE, we understand that every spa or wellness center has unique requirements. That’s why we offer extensive customization options for our massage beds for sale UAE, including:\\n<ul>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Adjustable sizes and dimensions to fit your space</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Choice of upholstery color and material</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Frame finishes and materials</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Optional accessories like armrests, headrests, or storage solutions</span></li>\\n</ul>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Our team works with clients to design a massage bed that meets both functional and aesthetic needs.</span>\\n<h2><b>High-Quality Materials and Craftsmanship</b></h2>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Durability and comfort are at the heart of our products. Each </span><b>massage bed in UAE</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> is built using premium materials, including reinforced steel or high-quality wood frames and dense foam padding. The upholstery is resistant to oils, lotions, and frequent cleaning, ensuring hygiene and longevity.</span>\\n\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Our skilled craftsmen focus on precision, stability, and attention to detail, creating massage tables that can withstand daily professional use while providing a luxurious feel for clients.</span>\\n<h2><b>Why Choose SPA Furniture?</b></h2>\\nAt SPA Furniture, we understand that a high-quality massage bed is the cornerstone of any professional wellness or therapy setup. Our products combine comfort, durability, and functionality to elevate both client experience and therapist efficiency. Here’s why SPA Furniture is the preferred choice in the UAE:\\n<ol>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><b>Professional Quality:</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> Our massage beds in UAE meet international standards for safety, strength, and comfort, ensuring stability and reliable performance for all treatments.</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><b>Expertise:</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> With years of experience, we design massage tables that are ergonomic, client-friendly, and optimized for smooth workflow in spas, salons, and wellness centers.</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><b>Customization Options:</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> Flexible options allow you to select dimensions, upholstery colors, and optional features like armrests or storage, tailoring your bed to your space and style.</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><b>Reliable Support:</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> From guidance and delivery to after-sales service, our team ensures a seamless purchase experience, helping you make a confident investment.</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><b>Trusted Supplier:</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> SPA Furniture is recognized across the UAE for professional-grade, long-lasting spa and therapy equipment, making us a reliable partner for wellness businesses.</span></li>\\n</ol>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Choosing SPA Furniture means investing in high-quality, ergonomic, and durable massage beds that enhance your services while creating a premium experience for clients.</span>\\n<h2><b>Massage Bed Price in UAE – What to Expect</b></h2>\\nThe massage bed price UAE varies depending on the type, features, and material. Manual models are cost-effective, while advanced electric massage tables in UAE may be priced higher due to multi-motor adjustments and premium finishes.\\n\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Investing in high-quality beds ensures longevity, reduces maintenance costs, and provides better service experiences for clients. SPA Furniture offers competitive pricing across all ranges without compromising quality.</span>\\n<h2><b>Industries We Serve</b></h2>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">SPA Furniture caters to a wide variety of industries across the UAE, including:</span>\\n<ul>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Luxury and boutique spas</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Physiotherapy and chiropractic clinics</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Beauty salons and wellness studios</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Hotel and resort spa facilities</span></li>\\n \\t<li style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\" aria-level=\\"1\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Mobile therapy practitioners</span></li>\\n</ul>\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Each sector benefits from our professional-grade massage beds, designed to meet industry-specific needs.</span>\\n<h2><b>Upgrade Your Wellness Space with SPA Furniture</b></h2>\\nChoosing the right massage bed for sale UAE is crucial for enhancing client experience and therapist efficiency. SPA Furniture provides versatile, durable, and ergonomic beds designed to meet professional standards in any spa, clinic, or wellness environment.\\n\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Whether you are looking for a manual massage table, a premium </span>electric massage bed in UAE<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">, or a portable solution, we have options to meet every requirement.</span>\\n\\n<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Contact SPA Furniture today to explore our range of professional massage beds in UAE and create the perfect wellness environment for your clients!</span>\\n<h2><b>FAQs</b></h2>\\n<ol>\\n \\t<li><b> What types of massage beds are available in UAE?</b><b>\\n</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">SPA Furniture offers manual, hydraulic, electric, low-height, portable, and specialized massage tables for professional use.</span></li>\\n \\t<li><b> How do I choose between a manual and electric massage bed?</b><b>\\n</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Electric beds are ideal for spas requiring motorized adjustments and advanced features, while manual beds are cost-effective and reliable for basic treatments.</span></li>\\n \\t<li><b> Can I customize the massage bed dimensions and color?</b><b>\\n</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Yes, SPA Furniture provides customization for frame finishes, upholstery colors, dimensions, and optional accessories to fit your workspace.</span></li>\\n \\t<li><b> How long do professional massage beds last?</b><b>\\n</b><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">High-quality beds with proper maintenance can last over 10 years, even in daily commercial use.</span></li>\\n \\t<li><b>Are SPA Furniture beds suitable for all spa treatments?</b>\\nYes, our beds are designed to accommodate general massages, Thai therapy, Reiki, prenatal, and other specialized treatment.</li>\\n</ol>\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_js][/vc_raw_js][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]\\n<h2>FAQ</h2>\\n[/vc_column_text][vc_tta_accordion c_position=\\"left\\" active_section=\\"\\" collapsible_all=\\"true\\"][vc_tta_section title=\\"1. What types of massage beds are available in UAE?\\" tab_id=\\"1777268477858-f26e80fa-3a0e\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">SPA Furniture offers manual, hydraulic, electric, low-height, portable, and specialized massage tables for professional use.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\\"2. How do I choose between a manual and electric massage bed?\\" tab_id=\\"1777268477872-f4f5dce4-7ece\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Electric beds are ideal for spas requiring motorized adjustments and advanced features, while manual beds are cost-effective and reliable for basic treatments.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\\"3. Can I customize the massage bed dimensions and color?\\" tab_id=\\"1777268511747-0efe6720-3f91\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Yes, SPA Furniture provides customization for frame finishes, upholstery colors, dimensions, and optional accessories to fit your workspace.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\\"4. How long do professional massage beds last?\\" tab_id=\\"1777268664547-e243eaa7-c44a\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">High-quality beds with proper maintenance can last over 10 years, even in daily commercial use.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\\"5. Are SPA Furniture beds suitable for all spa treatments?\\" tab_id=\\"1777268685842-312b0625-8f0a\\"][vc_column_text css=\\"\\"]<span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Yes, our beds are designed to accommodate general massages, Thai therapy, Reiki, prenatal, and other specialized treatment. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]"	PUBLISHED	2026-04-27 11:10:11	Buy Spa Massage Beds Online | High-Quality Spa Treatment Beds	Shop premium spa massage beds and spa beds online at Esthetica. Discover high-quality, ergonomic massage beds designed for comfort, style, and durability.	{"Massage Beds"}	\N	Massage Beds: Enhancing Comfort and Functionality at Esthetica	Find the ideal massage beds for your wellness center or private practice at Esthetica. Explore our premium electric spa massage tables and more.	\N	summary_large_image	\N	index,follow	\N	2026-06-05 07:16:00.684	2026-06-12 05:19:33.132
