{"title": "47", "mediaId": "cmqet7d83001rcg78d8q2iic4", "imagePath": "1781503529879-otmfmlahgw.png"}, {"title": "46", "mediaId": "cmqet7cxn001ncg78gdlae84t", "imagePath": "1781503529513-h0f1yr1hkvk.png"}, {"title": "45", "mediaId": "cmqet7co3001jcg787a6ep234", "imagePath": "1781503529169-8w21pnue034.png"}, {"title": "44", "mediaId": "cmqet7cey001fcg78mon079vm", "imagePath": "1781503528829-ne7r6hlhkf.png"}, {"title": "43", "mediaId": "cmqet7c4w001bcg78tvl632ht", "imagePath": "1781503528473-zczknh7kl8.png"}, {"title": "42", "mediaId": "cmqet7bvo0017cg7886dx1ea3", "imagePath": "1781503528131-6j0h1klt4ce.png"}, {"title": "41", "mediaId": "cmqet7ble0013cg78pbou7f97", "imagePath": "1781503527756-nidkii8hnx.png"}, {"title": "40", "mediaId": "cmqet7bb1000zcg78nnenreg8", "imagePath": "1781503527396-48mb9feabpn.png"}, {"title": "9", "mediaId": "cmqet7b1l000vcg78pc7t44az", "imagePath": "1781503527056-1v66va4p40u.png"}, {"title": "8", "mediaId": "cmqet7ari000rcg78ifxnw7xr", "imagePath": "1781503526671-t2xxb7zjhio.png"}, {"title": "7", "mediaId": "cmqet7agu000ncg78xpggfhko", "imagePath": "1781503526278-o2mbid13zag.png"}, {"title": "6", "mediaId": "cmqet7a63000jcg783hxn0d2w", "imagePath": "1781503525907-ow5q5nk956.png"}, {"title": "5", "mediaId": "cmqet79vm000fcg78gwaycu5w", "imagePath": "1781503525430-ncenaxx07yp.png"}], "title": "Across The Globe", "paragraphs": ["We are loved around the globe. Our products are used by World-Class spa and Hospitality brands like Marriott, WTS International, Hyatt, ITC, Six Senses, Four Seasons, Sun Siyam, Trident, Holiday Inn, Lux Resorts and many luxury spa projects across the globe.Our reputation as trusted spa furniture manufacturers is built on consistent quality, elegant design, and reliable global service. Leading wellness brands choose us not just for our products, but for the long-term value we bring to their spa environments."]}, "howWeDo": {"tag": "HOW WE DO", "logos": [{"title": "", "imagePath": "/assets/images/1.jpg"}, {"title": "", "imagePath": "/assets/images/2.jpg"}, {"title": "", "imagePath": "/assets/images/3.jpg"}, {"title": "", "imagePath": "/assets/images/4.jpg"}, {"title": "", "imagePath": "/assets/images/5.jpg"}, {"title": "", "imagePath": "/assets/images/6.jpg"}, {"title": "", "imagePath": "/assets/images/7.jpg"}, {"title": "", "imagePath": "/assets/images/8.jpg"}], "title": "What We Do", "paragraphs": ["Esthetica specializes in precision manufacturing luxury spa furniture, including high-end spa tables, massage bed ranges, spa treatment tables, and Ayurveda tables. We offer a comprehensive range of products tailored for hotel and resort spas. Our cutting-edge manufacturing facility boasts a modern setup. Esthetica handles every aspect of the manufacturing process with meticulous care and expertise. Your vision is our priority, and our capabilities span the entire spectrum of furniture production.\\n\\n", "Our in-house team works closely with architects, designers, and spa consultants to deliver solutions that meet global standards. As trusted massage table manufacturers and spa table manufacturers, we combine craftsmanship with innovation to provide spa furniture that performs beautifully, day after day."]}, "speciality": {"tag": "OUR SPECIALITY", "cards": [{"title": "", "imagePath": "/assets/images/speciality/wood.png"}, {"title": "", "imagePath": "/assets/images/speciality/finish.png"}, {"title": "", "mediaId": "cmq0rbqc005i6cgcb2d3mzriq", "imagePath": "1780653847792-53ep7u2pblk.png"}], "title": "Customised To Your Aesthetics", "description": "Our manufacturing unit empowers you to personalize your furniture down to the last detail. Choose from a spectrum of wood stain colours and upholstery options to create a piece that seamlessly integrates with your space. We can even customise the sizes as per your space requirements. This level of customization is ideal for spas and wellness centres seeking to align their interiors, treatment offerings, and client preferences. As experienced spa furniture manufacturers, we ensure that each product not only fits your space but also enhances its purpose and ambience."}, "productsIntro": {"tag": "OUR PRODUCTS", "body": "Explore our extensive collection, featuring high-end electric massage beds, specialized Spa Beds, Hydraulic Massage Tables, Spa Treatment Tables,  Ayurvedic Massage Tables, Spa Trolleys, Spa Stools, Relaxation Loungers, Ayurveda Panchakarma Table, Shirodhara & Abhyanga Table, Foot Reflexology Chairs, Manicure Tables, and Luxury Pedicure Chairs. Each piece is meticulously crafted to enhance the ambience and functionality of your spa.As one of the leading spa furniture manufacturers, massage table manufacturers, and massage bed suppliers in India, we offer customizable luxury spa furniture solutions that redefine the standards of comfort and design in modern spa furniture.", "heading": "Crafted till Perfection"}, "backgroundText": {"text": "Combining design innovation with aesthetics to redefine the standards of spa and wellness furniture. Our spa furniture adheres to the highest international quality standards, reflecting our unwavering commitment to delivering top-tier products.", "ctaHref": "/about/", "ctaLabel": "OUR BACKGROUND"}}	2026-06-19 12:25:26.176
